NK033(gi)004:1: // klong sde rdo rje zam pa las /
NK033(gi)004:2: nyams len bzhi'i rnal 'byor dang he ru ka mngon
NK033(gi)004:3: rdzogs rgyal po'i phrin las gsal bar bkod pa ye
NK033(gi)004:4: shes rgya mtsho zhes bya ba bzhugs so //
NK033(gi)004:5: na mo gu ru ma h+aa sh+r+ai he ru ka ya /
NK033(gi)004:6: chos kun ye nas dag pa'i klong chen por //
NK033(gi)004:7: ma skyes rang bzhin rdzogs pa'i dpal chen po //
NK033(gi)004:8: bde chen mdangs shar dbyings kyi yum dang bcas //
NK033(gi)004:9: rtsa brgyud bla ma'i tshul du bstan la 'dud //
NK033(gi)004:10: gsang chen yang rtse grub mchog gi //
NK033(gi)004:11: thugs kyi thig le mtshan tsam yang //
NK033(gi)004:12: rnyed dka' shin tu rnal 'byor gyi //
NK033(gi)004:13: dkyil 'khor las rim bltas chog dgod //
NK033(gi)004:14: rdzogs pa chen po sde gsum gyi nang tshan klong
NK033(gi)004:15: sde zam pa'i rnal 'byor nyams su len pa la
NK033(gi)004:16: bzhir gsungs te / ma dag pa dag par byed pa rgyam tsho khrus kyi lung /
NK033(gi)004:17: ma smin pa smin par byed pa sgo gsum las kyi spyod pa /
NK033(gi)004:18: ma grol ba grol bar byed pa sgom tshul bla ma'i byin rlabs /
NK033(gi)004:19: grol ba mthar phyin par byed pa snying po ye shes rdo rje'i rnal 'byor ro //
NK033(gi)004:20: de la thams cad kyi sngon du 'gro ba khrus lung la gnyis /
NK033(gi)004:24: stegs la tshom bu lnga bkod pa'i steng du rin
NK033(gi)004:25: po che'i bum par a mri ta dang gla rtsi
NK033(gi)004:26: min pa'i spos sman nyer lnga'i rdzas dag chu gsang
NK033(gi)004:27: gis bltams pa mgul chings kha rgyan gzungs thag bcas
NK033(gi)004:28: bzhag / bdag gi thugs kar +amo yig kha dog lnga ldan du gsal /
NK033(gi)004:29: +amo swa b+h+aa wa bi shud+d+hahsarba d+harmahswa b+h+aa wa bi shud+d+ho &aham /
NK033(gi)004:30: bum pa mi dmigs te stong par gyur /
NK033(gi)004:31: thugs ka'i las 'od 'phros lam ser po zhig tu gyur /
NK033(gi)004:32: de las gser gyi bum pa mtshan nyid dang ldan pa'i nang du pam las pad+ma'i sdong por gyur /
NK033(gi)004:33: de'i ze'u 'bru'i steng du rang gi thugs ka nas
NK033(gi)004:34: h+aum ljang gu zhig spros te yongs su gyur pa
NK033(gi)004:35: las / khro bo bdud rtsi 'khyil pa ljang sngon
NK033(gi)004:36: phyag gnyis dku la brten pa'i g.yas gser gyi rdo
NK033(gi)004:37: rje dang g.yon shel gyi dril bu bsnams pa /
NK033(gi)004:38: ba ti smug po gsol ba zhig tu gyur /
NK033(gi)004:39: yang rang gi thugs ka'i +amo las h+aum ljang gu 'phros /
NK033(gi)004:40: mdun gyi nam mkhar gong dang mtshungs pa'i bdud rtsi 'khyil bar gyur /
NK033(gi)004:42: bdag gi thugs ka nas 'od zer 'phros /
NK033(gi)004:43: mdun gyi lha la phog pas thugs rgyud bskul /
NK033(gi)004:44: de dag gi thugs ka nas 'od zer 'phros phyogs
NK033(gi)004:45: bcu'i de bzhin gshegs pa thams cad la phog pas
NK033(gi)004:46: mnyes nas sku gsung thugs kyi byin rlabs thams cad
NK033(gi)004:47: 'od zer gyi tshul du byon te nam mkha' bdud
NK033(gi)004:49: de las bdud rtsi'i rgyun babs /
NK033(gi)004:50: bum nang gi bdud rtsi 'khyil ba la phog /
NK033(gi)004:51: de'i sku las bdud rtsi'i rgyun babs pas bum pa gang bar gyur /
NK033(gi)004:57: bi ram shud+d+he shud+d+he a a a s+w+aa h+aa /
NK033(gi)004:58: sngags 'di ma dpe rnams su 'dra min mang bas yid brtan dka' 'dug /
NK033(gi)004:59: grangs ci nus bzlas pa'i mthar /
NK033(gi)004:60: bdud rtsi 'khyil ba dkar mer gyi zhu nas rim
NK033(gi)004:61: par thim ste bum chu dang dbyer med du 'dres
NK033(gi)004:62: pa'i steng du yi ge gsum byung bas bar chad
NK033(gi)004:64: lag pa g.yon pa'i mthe bos mathe'u chung mnan pa'i sor mo gsum bum pa'i kha la reg ste /
NK033(gi)004:66: mdzub mo la +aah srin lag la h+aum /
NK033(gi)004:69: de ltar bsgrub pa tshar nas las la sbyar ba ni /
NK033(gi)004:70: nangs par 'bru gsum brjod pas yig 'bru las 'od 'phros /
NK033(gi)004:71: shar nas na bza' dkar mo ke ke ru'i bum pa dkar po /
NK033(gi)004:72: lho nas spyan ma sngon mo bee d+aur+ya'i bum pa sngon po /
NK033(gi)004:73: nub nas m+aa ma k+ai dmar mo pad+ma r+aa ga'i bum pa dmar po /
NK033(gi)004:74: byang nas sgrol ma ljang gu mrgad kyi bum pa ljang gu thogs pa byon par mos /
NK033(gi)004:75: gung mdzub kyis bum pa'i mgrin pa nas bzung /
NK033(gi)004:76: khrus sngags brjod cing lag mthil du blugs /
NK033(gi)004:77: phud nam mkha' la gtor bas /
NK033(gi)004:78: bla ma yi dam mkha' 'gro dang sangs rgyas byang
NK033(gi)004:79: sems thams cad la bdud rtsi phul bas thugs dgyes
NK033(gi)004:80: nas dam tshig nyams chag thams cad dag cing rang
NK033(gi)004:81: la byin gyis brlabs par bsam /
NK033(gi)004:82: lha mo lngas bdud rtsi'i chu rgyun rang gi spyi
NK033(gi)004:83: bo nas mar blugs te khrus byas pas mos la
NK033(gi)004:84: / gdong bkrus pas lus kyi sgrib pa dag par bsam /
NK033(gi)004:85: kha bshal bas ngag gi sgrib pa dag par bsam /
NK033(gi)004:86: khong du btung bas yid kyi sgrib pa dag par bsam /
NK033(gi)004:87: de nas khyor ba gsum rim bzhin gtor la /
NK033(gi)004:88: 'dod khams kyi sgrib pa dag par gyur cig /
NK033(gi)004:89: gzugs khams kyi sgrib pa dag par gyur cig /
NK033(gi)004:90: gzugs med khams kyi sgrib pa dag par gyur cig /
NK033(gi)004:91: byas pas khams gsum gyi sems can thams cad kyi
NK033(gi)004:92: sgo gsum gyi sgrib pa dag nas nam mkha' lta
NK033(gi)004:95: nangs mo thog mar stong pa'i ngang las /
NK033(gi)004:96: rang gi lus 'di gser gyi bum pa /
NK033(gi)004:97: de nang pam las pad sdong /
NK033(gi)004:98: h+aum las rang sems bdud rtsi 'khyil ba /
NK033(gi)004:99: spyi bor yang bdud rtsi 'khyil ba bsgom pa'i khyad
NK033(gi)004:100: par tsam las gzhan dmigs bzlas yongs rdzogs gong dang
NK033(gi)004:101: 'dra bar byas / lha 'od du zhu rjes 'bru gsum gyi rgyas gdab /
NK033(gi)004:102: de nas snod gtsang mar chab btang la mdog nag
NK033(gi)004:103: dmar ljang gu rnams ngan pas gtsar sar phos la
NK033(gi)004:104: phyi khrus bya / dkar ser dang g.yas 'khor bzang bas /
NK033(gi)004:106: zhes brjod la srin lag gis dkrugs la mchod pa dang khrus sogs snga ma ltar bya'o //
NK033(gi)004:107: gnyis pa sgo gsum las kyi spyod pa la gsum /
NK033(gi)004:108: lus dwangs pa'i sgo nas phyag 'tshal /
NK033(gi)004:109: ngag dwangs pa'i sgo nas sngags bzlas /
NK033(gi)004:110: yid dwangs pa'i sgo nas bsam gtan bsgom pa'o //
NK033(gi)004:112: lag pa thal mo sbyar la /
NK033(gi)004:113: rang gi snying nang na +amo kha dog lnga dang ldan pa /
NK033(gi)004:114: de las 'od zer 'phros pas phyogs bcu'i sangs rgyas
NK033(gi)004:115: dang byang chub sems dpa' bla ma yi dam mkha'
NK033(gi)004:116: 'gro thams cad mdun gyi nam mkhar byon par bsam
NK033(gi)004:118: zhes se gol bsnol la brdab pa dang sngags brjod pa lan gsum bya /
NK033(gi)004:119: mdun gyi nam mkhar dgyes bzhin bzhugs par bsam /
NK033(gi)004:120: yang +amo las 'od zer byung thal mo'i nang du
NK033(gi)004:121: rin po che la sogs pa mchod pa'i rdzas dpag
NK033(gi)004:123: phyag re re bzhin rdzas rnams lan re phul bar bsam /
NK033(gi)004:124: bla ma la sogs pa'i zhabs la mgo bos gtugs
NK033(gi)004:125: pas sku gsung thugs las 'od zer byung lus ngag
NK033(gi)004:126: yid gsum gyi sgrib pa mtha' dag sangs sangs dag
NK033(gi)004:127: par bsam la / dkon mchog gsum la phyag 'tshal ba ni /
NK033(gi)004:128: yang dag par rdzogs pa'i sangs rgyas spang ba phun sum tshogs pa /
NK033(gi)004:129: ye shes phun sum tshogs pa'i bdag nyid dbyings dang
NK033(gi)004:130: ye shes gnyis su med pa la phyag 'tshal zhing
NK033(gi)004:131: skyabs su mchi'o // zhi ba mya ngan las 'das pa'i chos gsung rab yan lag bcu gnyis /
NK033(gi)004:133: yang dag pa'i don phyin ci ma log pa la phyag 'tshal zhing skyabs su mchi'o //
NK033(gi)004:134: 'phags pa'i dge 'dun sa chen po la rab tu
NK033(gi)004:135: bzhugs pa'i byang chub sems dpa' sems dpa' chen po
NK033(gi)004:136: phyir mi ldog pa rnams la phyag 'tshal zhing skyabs
NK033(gi)004:137: su mchi'o // de nas bla ma yi dam mkha'
NK033(gi)004:138: 'gro dang bstan pa'i bdag po la phyag 'tshal ba
NK033(gi)004:139: su mchi'o // / ma rig las kyis 'khor ba'i sems can rnams //
NK033(gi)004:140: nyon mongs nad kyis gdung ba la //
NK033(gi)004:141: chos kyi bdud rtsis gso mdzad pa //
NK033(gi)004:142: dus gsum bla ma rnams la gus par phyag 'tshal lo //
NK033(gi)004:143: rgyal ba thams cad dbyer med dbyings mnyam yang //
NK033(gi)004:144: bsnyen bkur dag gis mchod cing dbu la bkod //
NK033(gi)004:145: dngos grub rnam gnyis myur du ster mdzad pa'i //
NK033(gi)004:146: rigs lnga he ru ka la gus par phyag 'tshal lo //
NK033(gi)004:147: nam mkha'i lus can gar yang thogs med cing //
NK033(gi)004:148: 'dod par rgyug pa'i gzugs can 'phrul mo che //
NK033(gi)004:149: ma sring byams pa'i tshul gyis grogs mdzad ma //
NK033(gi)004:150: phyi nang mkha' 'gro'i tshogs la phyag 'tshal lo //
NK033(gi)004:151: dus gsum las kyi nang nas 'khor ba'i ru bzlog pa //
NK033(gi)004:152: nyon mongs thal ba'i gnas nas byang chub myu gu bskyed //
NK033(gi)004:153: srid dang 'das phyir 'gro ba'i don mdzad pa //
NK033(gi)004:154: bcom ldan lha yi lha la gus pas phyag 'tshal lo //
NK033(gi)004:157: dus gsum gyi bde bar gshegs pa thams cad kyi thugs kyi bcud bsdus pa'i snying po /
NK033(gi)004:159: zhes lan nyer gcig sogs brjod pa'i rang sgras bde
NK033(gi)004:160: bar gshegs pa rnams thugs dam gyi rgyud bskul zhing
NK033(gi)004:161: dgyes / sems can thams cad kyi sdig sgrib dag cing grol bar bsam /
NK033(gi)004:163: nam mkhar bzhugs pa'i sangs rgyas byang sems thams cad mkha' 'gro'i tshogs la bsdu /
NK033(gi)004:171: thig le'i bar du rim par bsdu /
NK033(gi)004:172: thig le smin mtshams kyi nam mkhar yod pa la sems bzung /
NK033(gi)004:174: +amo +aahmh'u barjooda pas spyi gtsug nas rtsa a wa
NK033(gi)004:175: d+h+au tir thim par bsam la brda bzhi'i tshul gyis
NK033(gi)004:177: gsum pa sgom tshul bla ma'i byin rlabs ni logs su bkod pa ltar ngo //
NK033(gi)004:178: bzhi pa snying po ye shes rdo rje'i rnal 'byor
NK033(gi)004:179: la bskyed rdzogs gnyis las 'dir bskyed pa'i phrin las
NK033(gi)004:184: gnas dben par rten dang dkyil 'khor skabs dang mthun par bkram /
NK033(gi)004:191: bla ma dang yi dam la re re /
NK033(gi)004:192: mkha' 'gro zhing skyes la sha lnga bdud rtsi lnga /
NK033(gi)004:194: sngags skyes la a mri tas brgyan pa bcas gsum bsham /
NK033(gi)004:195: sgrub pa po stan bde bar 'dug ste brgyud pa'i gsol 'debs bya /
NK033(gi)004:196: sgrub pa'i dbu brtsam pa sogs dgos pa yod na
NK033(gi)004:197: phyi rgyud la dkar gtor btang zhing phrin las bcol
NK033(gi)004:198: / bgegs la gtor ma bsngosa te bden pa brdar la bka' bsgo /
NK033(gi)004:199: +amo badz+ra yak+sha kro d+ha ha la ha la h'u /
NK033(gi)004:200: +amo sum+b+ha ni be ga ba ti rak+sha rak+sha h'u /
NK033(gi)004:201: zhes pa'i drag sngags lnga'am bdun brjod la bgegs bskrad /
NK033(gi)004:202: de nas skyabs su 'gro zhing byang chub tu sems bskyed pa ni /
NK033(gi)004:203: bla ma rdo rje slob dpon dang phyogs bcu na bzhugs pa'i sangs rgyas dang byang chub sems dpa' /
NK033(gi)004:204: dkyil 'khor gyi lha'i khyad par dang /
NK033(gi)004:205: gsang sngags yang dag gi lha tshogs rnams bdag la dgongs su gsol /
NK033(gi)004:206: bdag ming 'di zhes bgyi ba dus 'di nas bzung
NK033(gi)004:207: nas snying po byang chub la mchis kyi bar du
NK033(gi)004:209: sangs rgyas la skyabs su mchi'o //
NK033(gi)004:210: 'dod chags dang bral ba rnams kyi mchog /
NK033(gi)004:214: phyogs bcu na bzhugs pa'i de bzhin gshegs pa rnams la skyabs su mchi'o //
NK033(gi)004:215: de bzhin gshegs pa dgra bcom pa yang dag par
NK033(gi)004:216: rdzogs pa'i sangs rgyas sh+aakya thub pa la skyabs su
NK033(gi)004:217: mchi'o // mkhyen rab kyi bdag po 'phags pa 'jam dpal gzhon nur gyur pa la skyabs su mchi'o //
NK033(gi)004:218: thugs rje'i bdag po 'phags pa spyan ras gzigs dbang phyug la skyabs su mchi'o //
NK033(gi)004:219: mthu stobs kyi bdag po dpal phyag na rdo rje la skyabs su mchi'o //
NK033(gi)004:220: rdo rje slob dpon sangs rgyas dpal //
NK033(gi)004:221: dus gsum bzhugs la phyag 'tshal lo //
NK033(gi)004:222: dngos bshams yid kyis rnam sprul pa'i //
NK033(gi)004:223: dag pa'i mchod pa bzhes su gsol //
NK033(gi)004:224: dngos grub chu bo gcod pa'i gegs //
NK033(gi)004:225: nyes byas ma lus bshags par bgyi //
NK033(gi)004:226: dag pa'i mtha' bzhi dri ma med //
NK033(gi)004:227: rdzogs pa'i byang chub sems bskyed do //
NK033(gi)004:228: phyogs bcu 'khor gsum dag pa'i chos //
NK033(gi)004:229: ma chags spyod la rjes yi rang //
NK033(gi)004:230: mchog gsum bsten pa'i zhing gyur la //
NK033(gi)004:231: gnyis med yid kyis skyabs su mchi'o //
NK033(gi)004:232: bskul ba'i sa las bzhengs nas kyang //
NK033(gi)004:233: chos kyi 'khor lo bskor bar bskul //
NK033(gi)004:234: ma grol ba ni rnam grol phyir //
NK033(gi)004:236: bdag la gnas pa'i lus 'di ni //
NK033(gi)004:237: bde bar gshegs pa rnams la 'bul //
NK033(gi)004:238: tshe rabs bsags pa'i las rnams kun //
NK033(gi)004:239: bsdus te byang chub mchog tu bsngo //
NK033(gi)004:240: bsod nams 'di yis thams cad gzigs pa nyid //
NK033(gi)004:241: thob nas nyes pa'i dgra rnams bcom byas te //
NK033(gi)004:242: skye rga na 'chi'i rba klong 'khrugs pa yi //
NK033(gi)004:243: srid pa'i mtsho las 'gro ba sgrol bar shog /
NK033(gi)004:245: gnyis pa dgos gzhi lung rnam pa bdun gyis nub gcig gis phrin las gzhung bsrang ba la /
NK033(gi)004:246: dang po bgegs bsrung ba 'bar ba mtshams kyi lung du mtshams bcad pa la /
NK033(gi)004:252: bdag nyid skad cig gis dpal chen he ru ka
NK033(gi)004:253: gzi brjid bskal pa'i me ltar 'bar ba'i skur gyur
NK033(gi)004:255: dur khrod gsang ba mchog gi dkyil 'khor 'dir //
NK033(gi)004:256: yang dag don la mi brtson zhing //
NK033(gi)004:257: 'byung po dam med thams cad kun //
NK033(gi)004:258: rang rang gnas su bde bar dengs //
NK033(gi)004:260: bcom ldan dpal chen khros nas ni //
NK033(gi)004:261: bar chad sbyor ba thal bar rlog /
NK033(gi)004:262: mtshon cha 'bar ba'i gur gyis gtams //
NK033(gi)004:263: +amo badz+ra sh+r+ai he ru ka h'u phata /
NK033(gi)004:267: k+ai li k+ai la ya h'u phata /
NK033(gi)004:268: rang dpal he ru ka'i thugs ka nas 'od 'phros /
NK033(gi)004:270: phyogs mtshams thams cad ra ba dang gur gyis gtams par gyur pa'i phyi la me ri'o //
NK033(gi)004:271: +aa ko ta ya mung+ga ra h'u phata /
NK033(gi)004:273: rang gi thugs ka'i 'od zer las mtshon cha lnga'i tshogs spros pas bgegs thams cad tshar bcad /
NK033(gi)004:274: tshur 'dus pa las phyogs mtshams thams cad ra ba
NK033(gi)004:275: dang gur gyis gtams pa'i phyi rol du bskal pa'i
NK033(gi)004:276: me phung rab tu 'bar bar gyur /
NK033(gi)004:277: bsdu na de tsam gyi 'thus pas /
NK033(gi)004:281: steng yang rdo rje'i bla bre la //
NK033(gi)004:282: rdo rje'i thog dang ser chen 'bebs //
NK033(gi)004:283: 'og kyang rdo rje'i sa gzhi la //
NK033(gi)004:284: rdo rje'i sa gzhi gcal du bkram //
NK033(gi)004:285: bar snang rdo rje'i sprin phung 'khrigs //
NK033(gi)004:287: rdo rje'i glog 'khyug khyugs se khyug /
NK033(gi)004:288: rdo rje'i thog 'bebs lams se lam //
NK033(gi)004:289: rdo rje'i me 'bar ya la la //
NK033(gi)004:290: rdo rje'i tsh+wa tsh+wa skar ltar 'khrugs //
NK033(gi)004:291: phyogs mtshams steng 'og thams cad kun //
NK033(gi)004:292: thams cad rdo rje 'bar bas gtams //
NK033(gi)004:293: rdo rjes gtams pa'i gzhal yas 'dir //
NK033(gi)004:295: chu la zag pa'i gseng med cing //
NK033(gi)004:297: nyon cig bgegs dang log 'dren tshogs //
NK033(gi)004:300: bcom ldan dpal chen khros nas ni //
NK033(gi)004:301: bar chad sbyor ba thal bar rlog /
NK033(gi)004:302: rdo rje 'bar ba'i gur gyis gtams //
NK033(gi)004:304: steng yang phur pa'i bla bre la //
NK033(gi)004:306: steng yang dbyug to'i bla bre la //
NK033(gi)004:308: steng yang me yi bla bre la //
NK033(gi)004:309: me yi thog 'og kyang me yi me yis bar
NK033(gi)004:310: snang me yi me yi 'du 'phro rab tu 'bar
NK033(gi)004:311: // me yi glog me yi thog bskal pa'i me
NK033(gi)004:312: 'bar me yi tsh+wa phyogs mtshams thams cad me phung
NK033(gi)004:314: e ram phata ram dz+wa la ram /
NK033(gi)004:317: stong gsum stong gi 'jig rten na //
NK033(gi)004:318: phyogs bcu stong gi 'jig rten na //
NK033(gi)004:319: skye 'gro rtsi shing nags tshal kun //
NK033(gi)004:320: kun kyang rigs lnga khrag 'thung tshogs //
NK033(gi)004:321: khro bo'i sprul pas nam mkha' gang //
NK033(gi)004:322: khro mo'i sprul pas sa gzhi gang //
NK033(gi)004:323: ma tshogs dbang phyug bar snang gang //
NK033(gi)004:324: kun kyang rigs lnga khrag 'thung tshogs //
NK033(gi)004:325: rigs lnga'i mtshams las bgegs ma 'da' //
NK033(gi)004:326: rgya la 'da' na rdul du rlog /
NK033(gi)004:327: ces pa tsam gyi mthar sngags rnams brjod /
NK033(gi)004:328: rgyas par spro na re re bzhin sbyar te /
NK033(gi)004:331: dbus phyogs stong skye 'gro rtsi shing nags tshal kun //
NK033(gi)004:332: kun kyang bud+d+ha khro bo'i khro mo'i ma tshogs kun
NK033(gi)004:333: kyang bud+d+ha bud+d+ha'i mtshams las rgya la 'da' na rdul
NK033(gi)004:334: du rlog / +amo bud+d+ha sh+r+ai he ru ka bud+d+ha
NK033(gi)004:335: kro d+hi shwa ri s+t+wam ru lu ru lu h'u
NK033(gi)004:336: du rlog / b+h+yo h'u / bud+d+ha rak+sha rak+sha h'u /
NK033(gi)004:338: shar phyogs stong gi kun kyang badz+ra badz+ra sh+r+ai he
NK033(gi)004:339: ru ka badz+ra kro d+hi shwa ri s+t+wam ru lu
NK033(gi)004:340: ru lu badz+ra rak+sha rak+sha h'u /
NK033(gi)004:341: lho phyogs stong gi kun kyang rat+na rat+na sh+r+ai he
NK033(gi)004:342: ru ka rat+na kro d+hi shwa ri s+t+wam ru lu
NK033(gi)004:343: ru lu rat+na rak+sha rak+sha h'u /
NK033(gi)004:344: nub phyogs stong gi kun kyang pad+ma pad+ma sh+r+ai he
NK033(gi)004:345: ru ka pad+ma kro d+hi shwa ri s+t+wam ru lu
NK033(gi)004:346: ru lu pad+ma rak+sha rak+sha h'u /
NK033(gi)004:347: byang phyogs stong gi kun kyang karma karma sh+r+ai he
NK033(gi)004:348: ru ka karma kro d+hi shwa ri s+t+wam ru lu
NK033(gi)004:349: ru lu karma rak+sha rak+sha h'u /
NK033(gi)004:350: steng 'og mtshon cha dang khro bos bar mtshams med par gtams par bsam la /
NK033(gi)004:353: nga ni dpal chen he ru ka /
NK033(gi)004:354: nyon cig bgegs dang log 'dren tshogs //
NK033(gi)004:355: chos rnams rang bzhin ye nas stong pa las //
NK033(gi)004:356: rnam rtog 'khrul pa 'byung ba'i gzhi med de //
NK033(gi)004:357: bgegs kyang rang gi sems las byung //
NK033(gi)004:358: stong pa nyid kyis mtshams bcad do //
NK033(gi)004:359: bgegs zhes bya ba'i ming yang med //
NK033(gi)004:360: chos kyi dbyings kyis mtshams bcad do //
NK033(gi)004:361: zhes stong pa nyid kyi rgyas gdab bo //
NK033(gi)004:362: gnyis pa tshogs bsags sgrib sbyang gi lung du tha mal pas dbyangs dang bcas pas /
NK033(gi)004:364: mdun gyi nam mkhar yi dam rgyal ba zhi khro'i lha tshogs /
NK033(gi)004:368: mdun du chos skyong srung ma'i tshogs rnams gsal bar gyur /
NK033(gi)004:369: gdung shugs dbyangs dang bcas pas /
NK033(gi)004:371: dus gsum bde gshegs rnams kyi spyan snga ru //
NK033(gi)004:372: mtshan nyid don ma rtogs pa mthol lo bshags //
NK033(gi)004:373: brgyud pa'i bla ma rnams kyi spyan snga ru //
NK033(gi)004:374: dam tshig mos gus chung ba mthol lo bshags //
NK033(gi)004:375: yi dam lha tshogs rnams kyi spyan snga ru //
NK033(gi)004:376: bsnyen sgrub tshad du ma bskyal mthol lo bshags //
NK033(gi)004:377: dkyil 'khor lha tshogs rnams kyi spyan snga ru //
NK033(gi)004:378: mchod bstod gzhung ma skyong ba mthol lo bshags //
NK033(gi)004:379: ma sring mkha' 'gro rnams kyi spyan snga ru //
NK033(gi)004:380: gtor ma dus su ma theng mthol lo bshags //
NK033(gi)004:381: chos skyong srung ma rnams kyi spyan snga ru //
NK033(gi)004:382: dam rdzas tshang bar ma bsags mthol lo bshags //
NK033(gi)004:383: mched dang lcam dral rnams kyi spyan snga ru //
NK033(gi)004:384: dam tshig brtse gdung chung ba mthol lo bshags //
NK033(gi)004:385: dus gsum pha ma rnams kyi spyan snga ru //
NK033(gi)004:386: drin lan lan gyis ma lon mthol lo bshags //
NK033(gi)004:387: khams gsum sems can rnams kyi spyan snga ru //
NK033(gi)004:388: theg chen byang sems chung ba mthol lo bshags //
NK033(gi)004:389: zhes bshags pa dang bzod gsol bya'o //
NK033(gi)004:390: gsum pa mchod rdzas byin gyis brlab pa'i lung du sman brlab pa ni /
NK033(gi)004:392: stong pa'i ngang las yam ram kam las rlung me
NK033(gi)004:393: thod sgyed kyi steng du a las ka p+aa la
NK033(gi)004:394: yangs shing rgya che ba'i nang du rigs lnga yab
NK033(gi)004:395: yum gyi sa bon 'bru bcu las sha lnga bdud
NK033(gi)004:398: rdzas rnams zhu zhing 'dres pa'i rlangs pa las +aahmh'u
NK033(gi)004:399: gi 'od zer gyis ye shes kyi bdud rtsi bkug
NK033(gi)004:400: ste dam tshig gi rdzas dang ro gcig tu gyur
NK033(gi)004:401: / +aahmh'u sarba pany+tsa a mri ta h'u h+r+aihth+aa /
NK033(gi)004:404: stong pa'i ngang las a las b+hany+dza'i snod yangs shing
NK033(gi)004:405: rgya che ba'i nang du 'bru gsum 'od du zhu
NK033(gi)004:406: ba las bza' bca' btung ba 'dod pa'i yon tan
NK033(gi)004:407: ye shes lnga'i rang bzhin zad mi shes pa'i gter
NK033(gi)004:408: du gyur / +amo +aahmh'u ma h+aa ba lid+ha h'u h+r+aihth+aa /
NK033(gi)004:411: stong pa'i ngang las a las pad+ma'i b+hany+dza'i nang du
NK033(gi)004:412: ra las rgyu drug bsgral ba'i rak+ta'i rgya mtsho chen
NK033(gi)004:413: por gyur / +aahh+aum ma h+aa rak+ta dz+wa la man+dala la h+aum h+r+ai tha lnga'am bdun /
NK033(gi)004:417: rang rang gi ming yig dang po thig les brgyan
NK033(gi)004:418: pa las byung ba'i mchod pa'i lha mo mchod rdzas
NK033(gi)004:419: so so thogs pas nam mkha'i khams khengs par gyur
NK033(gi)004:428: de dag spyir brlab pa ni /
NK033(gi)004:429: +amo +aahmh'u badz+ra ma h+aa ka p+aa la kha kha /
NK033(gi)004:438: ma h+aa s+aa d+ha la h'u phata /
NK033(gi)004:439: ru lu ru lu h'u b+h+yo h'u /
NK033(gi)004:441: ma h+aa yo ga ad d+ha ma h+aa sa ma ya /
NK033(gi)004:442: a su ro hoh ka ma la sh+r+ai he ru /
NK033(gi)004:447: ma h+aa sa ma ya h'u phata /
NK033(gi)004:448: ru lu ru lu h'u b+h+yo h'u /
NK033(gi)004:449: zhes brjod la rol mo bya /
NK033(gi)004:450: spros pa la dga' na 'di'i gong du bab drug gis byin dbab kyang chog go //
NK033(gi)004:451: bzhi pa bdag nyid rtsa ba'i lung du yang dag mngon rdzogs zhi khro'i dkyil 'khor bskyed pa ni /
NK033(gi)004:452: dang po ting nge 'dzin rnam pa gsum bsgom pa las /
NK033(gi)004:455: 'di tshe sangs rgyas bsgrub bya'i phyir //
NK033(gi)004:456: sku gsum sa la goms par bya //
NK033(gi)004:457: dang po chos kyi dbyings nyid las //
NK033(gi)004:458: dmigs pa med pa'i don gcig bsgom //
NK033(gi)004:459: zhes dbyings spros bral nam mkha' lta bu'i ngang du mnyam par bzhag /
NK033(gi)004:461: chos kyi dbyings kyi ye shes kyis //
NK033(gi)004:462: thams cad du ni khyab par bsam //
NK033(gi)004:463: ye shes kyi rtsal snang snying rje chen pos sems can kun la khyab par bsgom /
NK033(gi)004:465: bskal pa'i me dpung 'khrugs pa bzhin //
NK033(gi)004:466: 'bar ba'i tshogs ni bsam par bya //
NK033(gi)004:467: stong nyid snying rje zung du 'jug pa las rang
NK033(gi)004:468: gi sems nyid +amo yig kha dog lnga ldan zhig
NK033(gi)004:469: tu gsal / de'ang thig le mthing /
NK033(gi)004:474: de las rten dang brten pa'i dkyil 'khor bskyed pa ni /
NK033(gi)004:475: rgyu'i +amo las e yam bam lam sum ram rnams rim par 'phros /
NK033(gi)004:476: e las chos kyi 'byung gnas gru gsum 'byams klas pa'i dbyings su /
NK033(gi)004:477: yam las rlung gi dkyil 'khor ljang gu zla gam /
NK033(gi)004:478: bam las chu'i dkyil 'khor zlum po dkar po /
NK033(gi)004:479: lam las gser gyi sa gzhi gru bzhi ser po /
NK033(gi)004:480: sum las rin po che sna bzhi las grub pa'i ri rab /
NK033(gi)004:481: ram las me dpung gi srung 'khor dang bcas pa
NK033(gi)004:482: ste 'byung ba lnga'i dkyil 'khor yum lnga'i mkha' klong
NK033(gi)004:484: ri rab kyi steng du b+h+r+aum spros pa las gzhal yas khang gdan dang bcas pa /
NK033(gi)004:485: de'i dbus su h+aum spros pa las dpal he ru ka'i skur gyur /
NK033(gi)004:486: de'ang don dam pa'i dbyings gcig la gdul bya'i snang
NK033(gi)004:487: bar sku dang zhing khams rnam pa lngar shar ba
NK033(gi)004:488: ste / +amo gu lam man+da la h'u /
NK033(gi)004:489: dbus kyi zhing khams ser po gser gyi rang bzhin /
NK033(gi)004:491: shar phyogs zhing khams dkar po ke ke ru'i rang bzhin /
NK033(gi)004:493: lho phyogs zhing khams sngon po bee d+aur+ya'i rang bzhin /
NK033(gi)004:494: +amo pad+ma r+aa ga man+da la h'u /
NK033(gi)004:495: nub phyogs zhing khams dmar po pad+ma r+aa ga'i rang bzhin /
NK033(gi)004:496: +amo in+d+ra n+ai la man+da la h'u /
NK033(gi)004:497: byang phyogs zhing khams ljang gu in+d+ra n+ai la'i rang bzhin /
NK033(gi)004:498: de lnga la pad+ma rab tu rgyas pa'i gdan lnga'i steng du a tsan+d+ra man+da la h'u /
NK033(gi)004:501: 'og nyi ma'i dkyil 'khor te de dag 'od zer 'bar ba'i gzhal yas khang re rer gyur /
NK033(gi)004:503: ba ti tish+tha man+da la h'u /
NK033(gi)004:504: chos 'byung bsnol ma zur drug pa /
NK033(gi)004:507: pad+ma'i gdan ge sar dang bcas 'od zer kha dog
NK033(gi)004:508: lnga 'phro ba la nyi zla dang dregs pa khyo
NK033(gi)004:509: shugs bsnol ba'i gdan rnams su gyur /
NK033(gi)004:510: +amo bud+d+ha sh+r+ai he ru ka bud+d+ha kro d+hi shwa ri s+t+wam /
NK033(gi)004:511: dbus su lha chen pho mo'i gdan la dpal mngon
NK033(gi)004:512: rdzogs rgyal po bud+d+ha he ru ka ser po gu
NK033(gi)004:513: lang gser btso ma'i mdog lta bu /
NK033(gi)004:514: yum swasti badz+ra bde ba stobs ldan mas 'khyud pa /
NK033(gi)004:515: +amo badz+ra sh+r+ai he ru ka badz+ra kro d+hi shwa ri s+t+wam /
NK033(gi)004:516: shar du dri za pho mo'i gdan la badz+ra he
NK033(gi)004:517: ru ka yab yum dkar po ke ke ru'i mdog
NK033(gi)004:518: can / +amo rat+na sh+r+ai he ru ka rat+na kro d+hi shwa ri s+t+wam /
NK033(gi)004:519: lhor gshin rje'i gdan la rat+na he ru ka yab yum sngon po bee d+aur+ya'i mdog can /
NK033(gi)004:520: +amo pad+ma sh+r+ai he ru ka pad+ma kro d+hi shwa ri s+t+wam /
NK033(gi)004:521: nub tu klu bdud kyi gdan la pad+ma he ru
NK033(gi)004:522: ka yab yum dmar po pad+ma r+aa ga'i mdog can
NK033(gi)004:523: / +amo karma sh+r+ai he ru ka karma kro d+hi shwa ri s+t+wam /
NK033(gi)004:524: byang du gnod sbyin gyi gdan la karma he ru
NK033(gi)004:525: ka yab yum ljang gu in+d+ra n+ai la'i mdog lta
NK033(gi)004:526: bu / thams cad kyang zhal gcig phyag gnyis /
NK033(gi)004:527: cung zad khros shing zhi ba'i mdangs dang ldan pa /
NK033(gi)004:528: yab rnams kyi phyag g.yas gser gyi rdo rje rtse
NK033(gi)004:529: dgu pa g.yon dril bu 'dzin pas yum la 'khyud
NK033(gi)004:530: pa / 'di sgrub thabs ltar yin la /
NK033(gi)004:532: g.yas gser gyi rdo rje rtse dgu pas g.yon ka
NK033(gi)004:533: p+aa la klad khrag gi gang ba dkrugs pa'i tshul
NK033(gi)004:535: dar ba ti sngon po'i sham thabs can /
NK033(gi)004:536: rin po che dang dur khrod kyi chas brgyad kyis brgyan pa /
NK033(gi)004:537: yab rnams kyi dbu skra phyed mthur du grol zhing zhabs brkyang bskum gyi tshul can /
NK033(gi)004:538: yum rnams skra grol zhing phyag mtshan yab dang 'dra bas mgul nas 'khyud pa /
NK033(gi)004:539: ye shes kyi rang 'od 'bar ba'i dbus na bzhugs pa /
NK033(gi)004:540: sangs rgyas rigs lngas dbu brgyan pa'o //
NK033(gi)004:541: de rnams kyang chos dbyings mngon rdzogs rgyal po gcig
NK033(gi)004:542: las ma g.yos kyang mos blos mthong tshul du phyogs
NK033(gi)004:543: gang nas bltas pa de dang mthun pa'i rigs kyi
NK033(gi)004:544: sku dang zhing khams su snang ba'o //
NK033(gi)004:551: tsan+di ka rnams kha dog sna tshogs pa /
NK033(gi)004:552: d+aa ma ru dang bdud rtsi'i thod pa bsnams shing kha t+w+aam ka dku la brten pa /
NK033(gi)004:553: zhabs g.yas brkyangs pa'i gar stabs kyis bzhugs pa'o //
NK033(gi)004:554: ru lu ru lu h'u b+h+yo h'u /
NK033(gi)004:555: de'i phyi rol du gnas kyi ma mo /
NK033(gi)004:558: dbang phyug ma nyi shu rtsa brgyad sogs sprul pa
NK033(gi)004:559: yang sprul dpag tu med pa nyi ma dang 'od
NK033(gi)004:560: zer gyi tshul du rang bzhin lhun grub kyi dkyil
NK033(gi)004:562: gzhung tshig gis gsal gdab pa ni /
NK033(gi)004:563: 'byung ba'i dkyil 'khor yum lnga'i mkha' dbyings su //
NK033(gi)004:564: mngon par dga' ba rin chen gzhal yas khang //
NK033(gi)004:565: nyi zla pad+ma 'od kyi kha sbyor nang //
NK033(gi)004:566: e bsnol zur drug ze'u 'bru brdal ba yi //
NK033(gi)004:567: dregs pa khyo shugs nyi zla pad+ma'i steng //
NK033(gi)004:568: mngon rdzogs rgyal po bud+d+ha he ru ka /
NK033(gi)004:569: zhal gcig phyag gnyis sku sngon ser //
NK033(gi)004:570: rin chen rgyan gyis rnam par brgyan //
NK033(gi)004:571: ba ti sngon po'i sham thabs can //
NK033(gi)004:572: dbu skra cung zad mthur du 'phyangs //
NK033(gi)004:573: zhi ba'i mdangs la cung zad khro //
NK033(gi)004:574: g.yas na rdo rje rtse dgu bsnams //
NK033(gi)004:575: g.yon na dngul dkar dril bu bsnams //
NK033(gi)004:576: phyag de gnyis kyis yum la 'khyud //
NK033(gi)004:577: yum bde stobs dang ldan pa ni //
NK033(gi)004:579: sku mdog yab 'dra dbu skra grol //
NK033(gi)004:580: bdag nyid gsal ba'i thugs ka nas //
NK033(gi)004:581: yi ge +amo ni kha dog lnga //
NK033(gi)004:582: shin tu gsal bar bsgom par bya //
NK033(gi)004:583: shar phyogs zhing khams dkar po la //
NK033(gi)004:584: badz+ra he ru yab yum dkar //
NK033(gi)004:585: lho phyogs zhing khams mthing ga la //
NK033(gi)004:586: rat+na he ru yab yum mthing //
NK033(gi)004:587: nub phyogs zhing khams dmar po la //
NK033(gi)004:588: pad+ma he ru yab yum dmar //
NK033(gi)004:589: byang phyogs zhing khams ljang gu la //
NK033(gi)004:590: karma he ru yab yum ljang //
NK033(gi)004:591: 'bar ba'i gar dgu khro tshul rdzogs //
NK033(gi)004:592: skad cig dran rdzogs tsam gyis ni //
NK033(gi)004:593: rnam pa lha la rang bzhin med //
NK033(gi)004:594: mtshan nyid spros pa thams cad bral //
NK033(gi)004:595: bde gsal mi rtog dbyings kyi ngang //
NK033(gi)004:596: gang nas bltas pa de ltar snang //
NK033(gi)004:597: don la dpal chen gcig nyid du //
NK033(gi)004:598: mngon rdzogs rgyal po che ba'i mchog /
NK033(gi)004:599: spyi dpal bla na med pa'o //
NK033(gi)004:600: de dag gis bskyed pa'i rnal 'byor song nas /
NK033(gi)004:601: de nyid rdzogs byed kyi yan lag drag bstim mchod
NK033(gi)004:602: bshags rnams bya dgos pas thog mar ye shes pa
NK033(gi)004:604: de ltar gsal ba'i thugs ka'i 'od zer gyis 'og min nas ye shes pa spyan drang par gyur /
NK033(gi)004:606: 'og min bde gshegs pho brang nas //
NK033(gi)004:608: gnas 'dir brtse phyir gshegs su gsol //
NK033(gi)004:609: +amo e h+ye hi bud+d+ha sh+r+ai he ru ka bud+d+ha kro d+hi shwa ri s+t+wam /
NK033(gi)004:610: +amo ru lu ru lu h'u b+h+yo h'u /
NK033(gi)004:612: mdun gyi nam mkhar bzhugs pa la dam tshig pas phyag byas par bsam la /
NK033(gi)004:614: mi gnas mi dmigs chos sku dag pa las //
NK033(gi)004:615: bdud 'dul khro tshogs dag pa'i sku sprul pa //
NK033(gi)004:616: bcom ldan dpal chen 'khor dang bcas pa la //
NK033(gi)004:617: gnyis su med pa'i tshul gyis phyag 'tshal lo //
NK033(gi)004:618: a la la hoh a ti p+au hoh pra t+aits+tsha hoh ya mi na mo /
NK033(gi)004:619: phyag byas pas lha ye shes sems dpa' dgyes nas
NK033(gi)004:620: sku gsung thugs kyis bdag dam tshig sems dpa'i lus
NK033(gi)004:621: ngag yid gsum byin gyis brlabs par bsam mo //
NK033(gi)004:622: de nas bzhugs su gsol ba ni /
NK033(gi)004:623: sems can don phyir nan tan mchog bskyed cing //
NK033(gi)004:624: ye shes thugs rjes bdag la dgongs nas kyang //
NK033(gi)004:625: bcom ldan dpal chen he ru 'khor dang bcas //
NK033(gi)004:626: dngos grub stsol phyir brtan par bzhugs su gsol //
NK033(gi)004:628: ye shes pa rnams dam tshig pa gtso 'khor so
NK033(gi)004:629: so la thim pas gzi brjid nus pa dang ldan
NK033(gi)004:630: par bsam / de nas phyag rgya gar gyi mchod pa 'bul ba ni /
NK033(gi)004:632: phyogs bcu'i 'jig rten thams cad na //
NK033(gi)004:633: bcom ldan dpal gyi phyag rgyar gsal //
NK033(gi)004:634: sku gsum gnyis med bde chen rgya //
NK033(gi)004:635: phyag rgya gar gyi mchod pa bzhes //
NK033(gi)004:636: a la la hoh zhes snang srid thams cad dpal chen po'i skur gsal bar blta'o //
NK033(gi)004:637: de nas rigs lnga'i he ru ka la bstod cing bshags pa bya ba ni /
NK033(gi)004:639: dbus phyogs gu lang gser gyi zhing khams na //
NK033(gi)004:640: nyi ma stong gi 'od zer shar ba bzhin //
NK033(gi)004:641: bud+d+ha he ru ka 'od kyi dkyil 'khor du //
NK033(gi)004:642: dpal ldan gzi brjid 'bar la phyag 'tshal bstod //
NK033(gi)004:643: sems nyid mnyam pa nyid kyi don ma rtogs //
NK033(gi)004:644: sems nyid mnyam pa nyid kyi don rtogs su //
NK033(gi)004:645: rang sems byang chub sems su ma 'byongs pas //
NK033(gi)004:646: bdud rtsi chen po lags par ngo ma shes //
NK033(gi)004:647: dngos grub chen po lags par zhal ma 'dzom //
NK033(gi)004:648: de yang mi 'chab gnong ba'i sems kyis mthol lo bshags //
NK033(gi)004:649: mthol bshags bzod pa dang du yar bzhes la //
NK033(gi)004:650: mi sgrib tshangs pa'i dngos grub stsal tu gsol //

NK033(gi)004:652: nyi ma stong gi 'od zer shar ba bzhin //

NK033(gi)004:654: dpal ldan gzi brjid 'bar la phyag 'tshal bstod //

NK033(gi)004:684: de yang mi 'chab gnong pa'i sems kyis mthol lo bshags //
NK033(gi)004:685: mthol bshags bzod pa dang du yar bzhes la //
NK033(gi)004:686: mi sgrib tshangs pa'i dngos grub stsal tu gsol //
NK033(gi)004:687: byang phyogs in+d+ra n+ai la ljang gu'i zhing khams na //
NK033(gi)004:688: nyi ma stong gi 'od zer shar ba bzhin //
NK033(gi)004:689: karma he ru ka 'od kyi dkyil 'khor du //
NK033(gi)004:690: dpal ldan gzi brjid 'bar la phyag 'tshal bstod //
NK033(gi)004:691: sems nyid mnyam pa nyid kyi don ma rtogs //
NK033(gi)004:692: sems nyid mnyam pa nyid kyi don rtogs su //
NK033(gi)004:693: rang sems byang chub sems su ma 'byongs pas //
NK033(gi)004:694: bdud rtsi chen po lags par ngo ma shes //
NK033(gi)004:695: dngos grub chen po lags par zhal ma 'dzom //
NK033(gi)004:696: de yang mi 'chab gnong ba'i sems kyis mthol lo bshags //
NK033(gi)004:697: mthol bshags bzod pa dang du yar bzhes la //
NK033(gi)004:698: mi sgrib tshangs pa'i dngos grub stsal du gsol //
NK033(gi)004:699: de nas phyi'i mchod pa rnam pa lnga 'bul ba ni /
NK033(gi)004:700: rang gi thugs ka nas mchod pa'i lha mo rnams
NK033(gi)004:701: rim par spros te mchod pa gnas so sor phul
NK033(gi)004:703: +amo bud+d+ha sh+r+ai he ru ka bud+d+ha kro d+hi shwa ri s+t+wam /
NK033(gi)004:706: +amo bud+d+ha sogs lha sngags re re bzhin mchod sngags kyi 'gor sbyar la /

NK033(gi)004:711: +amo badz+ra +aa lo ke pra t+aits+tsha h'u /
NK033(gi)004:715: +amo badz+ra nee wi d+ya pra t+aits+tsha h+aum /
NK033(gi)004:719: mngon rdzogs yab yum 'khor bcas la //
NK033(gi)004:720: mchod pa 'bul lo bzhes su gsol //
NK033(gi)004:721: +amo ru lu ru lu h'u b+h+yo h+aum /
NK033(gi)004:724: +amo badz+ra sh+r+ai he ru ka badz+ra kro d+hi shwa ri s+t+wam /
NK033(gi)004:727: shap+da'i bar so sor sbyar ba'i mthar /
NK033(gi)004:728: badz+ra khrag 'thung yab yum sogs tshig rkang gnyis sngags bcas /
NK033(gi)004:729: +amo rat+na sh+r+ai sogs mchod sngags dang /
NK033(gi)004:731: +amo pad+ma sh+r+ai sogs mchod sngags dang /
NK033(gi)004:733: +amo karma sh+r+ai sogs mchod sngags dang /
NK033(gi)004:734: karma khrag 'thung yab yum sogs so sor sbyar /
NK033(gi)004:735: de nas gong gi mchod pa byin rlabs sngags /
NK033(gi)004:736: +amo +aahmh'u badz+ra ma h+aa ka p+aa la sogs kyi mthar /
NK033(gi)004:739: a smin pa la ya pa to hoh a la la hoh zhes btags pas kyang mchod /
NK033(gi)004:740: de nas sman mchod 'bul ba ni /
NK033(gi)004:741: byin gyis brlabs pa'i sman phud sbreng la /
NK033(gi)004:743: ngo mtshar rmad du byung ba'i dkyil 'khor 'dir //
NK033(gi)004:744: 'byung ba'i bcud bsdus 'bras bu bdud rtsi'i bcud //
NK033(gi)004:745: yum chen m+aa ma k+ai ru byin brlabs nas //
NK033(gi)004:746: rgya mtsho chu klung mtsho bran man chad nas //
NK033(gi)004:747: zil pa'i thig pa'i brlan gyi bcud bsdus te //
NK033(gi)004:748: 'bru bcud stong la sbyar ba'i dza gad dpa' bos bkang //
NK033(gi)004:749: dus gsum rgyal ba yab yum mchod pa dang //
NK033(gi)004:750: rgyal ba rgya mtsho'i thugs dam bskang ba dang //
NK033(gi)004:751: 'gro ba ma lus thugs rjes bzung ba'i phyir //
NK033(gi)004:752: nyon mongs dug lnga sel ba'i bdud rtsi 'di //
NK033(gi)004:753: ji snyed bla ma yi dam dang //
NK033(gi)004:755: bdag cag dad pas 'bul lags na //
NK033(gi)004:756: thugs rjes dgongs la bzhes su gsol //
NK033(gi)004:757: brgyud pa'i bla ma rnams kyi zhal du +amo +aahmh'u /
NK033(gi)004:758: sarba pany+tsa a mri ta kha ram kh+aa hi /
NK033(gi)004:759: bcom ldan dpal chen yab yum dang /
NK033(gi)004:760: lha mo brgyad kyi zhal du +amo +aahmh'u /
NK033(gi)004:761: sarba pany+tsa a mri ta kha ram kh+aa hi /
NK033(gi)004:764: dbang phyug nyi shu rtsa brgyad /
NK033(gi)004:766: zhi khro'i lha tshogs rnams kyi zhal du +amo +aahmh'u /
NK033(gi)004:767: sarba pany+tsa a mri ta kha ram kh+aa hi /
NK033(gi)004:769: sku gsung thugs mnyes nas thod pa'i nang du dngos grub +amo +aahmh'u byung /
NK033(gi)004:770: rang gi mtheb srin gyis blangs la lce thog tu
NK033(gi)004:771: bzhag pas sku gsung thugs kyi dngos grub thob par
NK033(gi)004:774: dpa' bo 'bru gsum tshul du ni //
NK033(gi)004:775: sku gsung thugs kyi dngos grub 'di //
NK033(gi)004:776: sgrub mchog bdag la stsal tu gsol //
NK033(gi)004:778: w+aa ka sid+d+hi +aah tsit+ta sid+d+hi h'u /
NK033(gi)004:779: zhes gnas gsum du thig le bya'o //
NK033(gi)004:780: de nas gtor ma la dus bzhir gsungs pa las 'dir mchod gtor gyi dus ltar dmigs la /
NK033(gi)004:783: dpal chen yab yum mchod pa dang //
NK033(gi)004:784: ma sring rgya mtsho ma lus brten pa dang //
NK033(gi)004:785: rdo rje rgyal po rgyal thebs king ka ra //
NK033(gi)004:786: mched lcam 'dus pa'i g.yar dam bskang ba'i phyir //
NK033(gi)004:787: rin chen tshang ba'i gtor gzhong chen po ru //
NK033(gi)004:788: zhal zas bdud rtsi sha chen dang //
NK033(gi)004:789: rak+ta dmar dang dkar gyis brgyan //
NK033(gi)004:791: zhing khams rgyas par bkang nas 'bul lags na //
NK033(gi)004:792: sngags bdag chen pos byin gyis brlab tu gsol //
NK033(gi)004:793: zhes gtor mar sman raka sbreng ngo //
NK033(gi)004:794: brgyud pa'i bla ma rnams kyi zhal du ma h+aa ba lim ta kha ram kh+aa hi /
NK033(gi)004:795: bud+d+ha sh+r+ai he ru ka bud+d+ha kro d+hi shwa ri s+t+wam /
NK033(gi)004:796: ma h+aa ba lim ta kha ram kh+aa hi /
NK033(gi)004:797: badz+ra sh+r+ai he ru ka badz+ra kro d+hi shwa ri s+t+wam /
NK033(gi)004:798: ma h+aa ba lim ta kha ram kh+aa hi /
NK033(gi)004:799: rat+na sh+r+ai he ru ka rat+na kro d+hi shwa ri s+t+wam /
NK033(gi)004:800: ma h+aa ba ling+ta kha ram kh+aa hi /
NK033(gi)004:801: pad+ma sh+r+ai he ru ka pad+ma kro d+hi shwa ri s+t+wam /
NK033(gi)004:802: ma h+aa ba lim ta kha ram kh+aa hi /
NK033(gi)004:803: karma sh+r+ai he ru ka karma kro d+hi shwa ri s+t+wam /
NK033(gi)004:804: ma h+aa ba lim ta kha ram kh+aa hi /
NK033(gi)004:808: dbang phyug nyi shu brtsa brgyad /
NK033(gi)004:810: zhi khro'i lha tshogs rnams kyi zhal du ma h+aa ba lim ta kha ram kh+aa hi /
NK033(gi)004:811: zhes stong gsum bdud rtsir bsgyur ba'i bcud thams cad bsdus nas so so'i zhal du stob par bsam /
NK033(gi)004:813: chang phud dang sbyar te 'bul la /
NK033(gi)004:815: rnal 'byor dbang phyug dgongs pa bsgrub pa dang //
NK033(gi)004:816: ma sring rgya mtsho ma lus brten pa dang //
NK033(gi)004:817: dpal chen ma mo'i thugs dam bskang ba'i phyir //
NK033(gi)004:818: pad+ma zil thig dri dang sbyar ba yis //
NK033(gi)004:819: dung chen dmar gyis bkang ba'i rak+ta 'di //
NK033(gi)004:820: mnga' bdag chen pos bzhes la byin gyis rlobs //
NK033(gi)004:821: zhes pas gtor mar sgreng ngo //
NK033(gi)004:824: thugs rje chags pa'i rang bzhin gyis //
NK033(gi)004:825: 'gro ba'i don la dmigs pa yi //
NK033(gi)004:827: bla ma bde gshegs mkha' 'gro dang //
NK033(gi)004:828: chos skyong srung ma ma lus la //
NK033(gi)004:829: brtse ba'i sems kyis 'bul lags kyi //
NK033(gi)004:830: thugs rjes dgongs la bzhes su gsol //
NK033(gi)004:831: ma h+aa rak+ta kha ram kh+aa hi /
NK033(gi)004:833: bdud rtsi'i rgya mtsho chen po phul bas mnyes par bsam /
NK033(gi)004:835: de nas phyag rgya gar gyi mchod pa ni /
NK033(gi)004:836: dpal chen yab yum rnams kyi sku shin tu gsal bar bltas la /
NK033(gi)004:838: mi gnas dpal chen mngon rdzogs he ru ka /
NK033(gi)004:839: lha mo brgyad kyis bskor ba'i dkyil 'khor 'dir //
NK033(gi)004:840: rnam dag chos sku'i ngang las ma g.yos kyang //
NK033(gi)004:841: sgyu ma'i phyag rgya gsal la phyag 'tshal bstod //
NK033(gi)004:842: ces yi ge brgya pa tshar gcig brjod /
NK033(gi)004:843: de nas kha bskang ba'i phyir bshags pa bya ba ni /
NK033(gi)004:845: ye shes mkha' 'gro'i dbang phyug khro rgyal gtso //
NK033(gi)004:846: dpal chen he ru ka ni mtha' dang mnyam //
NK033(gi)004:847: dus drug chos kyi sku las ma g.yos kyang //
NK033(gi)004:848: thugs dang 'gal ba mchis na bzod par gsol //
NK033(gi)004:849: ye shes lha la rtog pa mi mnga' yang //
NK033(gi)004:850: de yi 'khor du gtogs pa'i lha srin rnams //
NK033(gi)004:851: gnong zhing 'gal 'khrul mchis pa mthol lo bshags //
NK033(gi)004:852: rig 'dzin sgrub pa po ni chos nyid thugs su chud //
NK033(gi)004:853: ma rig dbang gis de ltar ma rtogs kyang //
NK033(gi)004:854: mi dge log pa'i las rnams ci bgyis pa //
NK033(gi)004:855: bstan pa srung ba rnams la bzod par gsol //
NK033(gi)004:856: 'da' ka khas blang dam las g.yel gyur te //
NK033(gi)004:857: rdo rje sems dpa'i thugs dang ci 'gal ba //
NK033(gi)004:858: thugs rje che mnga' khyed la bzod par gsol //
NK033(gi)004:859: sbyor sgrol mchod pa ting 'dzin ma bshams te //
NK033(gi)004:860: kro d+hi shwa ri'i thugs dang ci 'gal ba //
NK033(gi)004:861: thugs rje che mnga' khyed la bzod par gsol //
NK033(gi)004:862: rdzas dang phyag rgya mngon du ma gyur te //
NK033(gi)004:863: koo r+ai ma brgyad thugs dang ci 'gal ba //
NK033(gi)004:864: thugs rje che mnga' khyed la bzod par gsol //
NK033(gi)004:865: sha khrag mchod pa gzhung bzhin ma bshams pas //
NK033(gi)004:866: sing+ha ma brgyad thugs dang ci 'gal ba //
NK033(gi)004:867: thugs rje che mnga' khyed la bzod par gsol //
NK033(gi)004:868: shar lho nub byang sgo bzhi ma gsal te //
NK033(gi)004:869: lta gdong sgo ma bzhi yi thugs dang ci 'gal ba //
NK033(gi)004:870: thugs rje che mnga' khyed la bzod par gsol //
NK033(gi)004:871: yo byad tshogs nas tshogs kyi phud nyams pas //
NK033(gi)004:872: mkha' 'gro dbang phyug thugs dang ci 'gal ba //
NK033(gi)004:873: thugs rje che mnga' khyed la bzod par gsol //
NK033(gi)004:874: tshogs la rol nas lhag ma ma lus pas //
NK033(gi)004:875: ma mo brtan ma'i thugs dang ci 'gal ba //
NK033(gi)004:876: thugs rje che mnga' khyed la bzod par gsol //
NK033(gi)004:877: sku bskyed khro bo'i lus su ma gyur pas //
NK033(gi)004:878: sngags 'jug pho nya'i thugs dang ci 'gal ba //
NK033(gi)004:879: thugs rje che mnga' khyed la bzod par gsol //
NK033(gi)004:880: zhes me tog dor la bzod gsol bya'o //
NK033(gi)004:881: don lnga pa yang dag thugs kyi mngon rdzogs rgyal po la 'dzab dbul ba ni /
NK033(gi)004:882: bzlas brjod bsnyen pa'i lung du ru lu'i 'dzab bgrang
NK033(gi)004:883: bar bya ste ru lu dbyangs kyi 'dren stangs drug
NK033(gi)004:885: 'dir phreng ba sngags kyi rnal 'byor bsgom pa ni /
NK033(gi)004:886: bdag gi thugs kar sna tshogs rdo rje'i lte ba na /
NK033(gi)004:892: 'a ljang gu de'i mthar g.yas bskor du bzla bya'i sngags kyis bskor bar dmigs la /
NK033(gi)004:894: +amo bud+d+ha sh+r+ai he ru ka bud+d+ha kro d+hi shwa ri s+t+wam /
NK033(gi)004:895: ru lu ru lu h'u b+h+yo h+aum /
NK033(gi)004:897: +amo pad+ma sh+r+ai he ru ka pad+ma kro d+hi shwa ri s+t+wam /
NK033(gi)004:898: ru lu ru lu h'u b+h+yo h'u /
NK033(gi)004:900: +amo badz+ra sh+r+ai he ru ka badz+ra kro d+hi shwa ri s+t+wam /
NK033(gi)004:901: ru lu ru lu h'u b+h+yo h'u /
NK033(gi)004:903: +amo rat+na sh+r+ai he ru ka rat+na kro d+hi shwa ri s+t+wam /
NK033(gi)004:904: ru lu ru lu h'u b+h+yo h'u /
NK033(gi)004:906: +amo karma sh+r+ai he ru ka karma kro d+hi shwa ri s+t+wam /
NK033(gi)004:907: ru lu ru lu h'u b+h+yo h+aum /
NK033(gi)004:908: zhes sngags tshan lnga po cha snyoms su gsal ba dod par bzla /
NK033(gi)004:909: de'ang dus bzhir ting nge 'dzin dang ma bral bar bzla ba'i thun dang po la bsnyen pa /
NK033(gi)004:912: bzhi par sgrub pa chen po'i tshul du byed pa las /
NK033(gi)004:914: bzhi pa ni sgom tshul bla ma'i byin rlabs dang
NK033(gi)004:915: 'brel ba ste de'i tshul gzhan du bkod pa ltar
NK033(gi)004:916: ro // de dag gi dus su rnam pa lha'i phyag rgya /
NK033(gi)004:917: rang bzhin skye ba med pa /
NK033(gi)004:918: nyams myong bde ba chen por shar ba la rnal 'byor rtse gcig tu bya'o //
NK033(gi)004:919: bzlas pa grub nas kha skor dang bcas mchod bstod mdor bsdus spyi ltar spros kyang 'gal ba med /
NK033(gi)004:920: 'dir nges par gtor chog bya bar gsungs pas /
NK033(gi)004:922: bdag gi thugs kar +amo kha dog lnga dang ldan
NK033(gi)004:923: pa las ma dmar ser gcig lag pa g.yon pa'i
NK033(gi)004:924: mthil du byung / nyi ma'i dkyil 'khor du gyur /
NK033(gi)004:926: yang a dkar po lag pa g.yas pa'i mthil du byung /
NK033(gi)004:930: yang h'u sngon po zhig 'phros mtheb chen sbrel ba'i
NK033(gi)004:931: bar du mgo mthur la bstan pas gtor ma lan
NK033(gi)004:932: gsum du dkrugs pas dam tshig gi bdud rtsir gyur
NK033(gi)004:935: g.yon pa'i nyi dkyil las bdud rtsi babs /
NK033(gi)004:938: g.yas kyi zla dkyil las bdud rtsi babs /
NK033(gi)004:941: g.yas bskor du dkrugs tshul bya /
NK033(gi)004:942: gtor ma bdud rtsi'i rgya mtsho kha dog dri bsung
NK033(gi)004:943: phun sum tshogs pa ro mchog brgya dang ldan par
NK033(gi)004:944: gyur / +amo ma h+aa ba lim ta te dzo
NK033(gi)004:945: ba lim ta ba la ba te gu h+ya sa
NK033(gi)004:946: ma ye sat+wa h'u s+w+aa h+aa /
NK033(gi)004:948: gtor mgron bla ma yi dam mkha' 'gro mdun gyi nam mkhar spyan drangs par bsam /
NK033(gi)004:949: 'bar ba'i phyag rgya smin mtshams su bskor la /
NK033(gi)004:950: +amo gu ru d+aa ki ni h'u h'u sa m+aa
NK033(gi)004:951: dzah +amo d+he ba d+aa ki n+ai h'u h'u sa
NK033(gi)004:952: m+aa dzah +amo dzo ki d+aa ki ni h'u h'u
NK033(gi)004:957: de nas gtor ma 'bul ba ni /
NK033(gi)004:958: lha tshogs rnams kyi ljags rdo rje'i sbu gus gtor
NK033(gi)004:959: ma'i bdud rtsi drangs te gsol bas mnyes par gyur
NK033(gi)004:960: par bsam la / +amo gu ru d+aa ki ni
NK033(gi)004:961: ye i dam ba lim ta kha kha kh+aa hi
NK033(gi)004:962: par bsam la / kh+aa hi / +amo d+he wa
NK033(gi)004:963: d+aa ki ni ye i dam ba lim ta kha
NK033(gi)004:965: +amo dzo ki d+aa n+ai ye i dam ba lim ta kha kha kh+aa hi kh+aa hi /
NK033(gi)004:966: re re la lan gsum gsum brjod do //
NK033(gi)004:967: de nas tshigs bcad kyis dbul ba ni /
NK033(gi)004:968: byin gyis rlob pa'i bla ma dam pa rnams kyi
NK033(gi)004:969: zhal du dam rdzas bdud rtsi 'bar ba'i mchod pa
NK033(gi)004:970: bzhes shig kha ram kh+aa hi /
NK033(gi)004:971: rim pa dbang gi bla ma dam pa rnams kyi
NK033(gi)004:972: zhal du dam rdzas bdud rtsi 'bar ba'i mchod pa
NK033(gi)004:973: bzhes shig kha ram kh+aa hi /
NK033(gi)004:974: shes rgyud grol ba'i bla ma dam pa rnams kyi
NK033(gi)004:975: zhal du dam rdzas bdud rtsi 'bar ba'i mchod pa
NK033(gi)004:977: nges par ston pa'i bla ma dam pa rnams kyi
NK033(gi)004:978: zhal du dam rdzas bdud rtsi 'bar ba'i mchod pa
NK033(gi)004:979: bud+d+he he ru ka'i zhal du dam rdzas bdud rtsi
NK033(gi)004:980: 'bar ba'i mchod pa badz+ra he ru ka'i zhal du
NK033(gi)004:981: dam rdzas bdud rtsi 'bar ba'i mchod pa rat+na he
NK033(gi)004:982: ru ka'i zhal du dam rdzas bdud rtsi 'bar ba'i
NK033(gi)004:983: mchod pa pad+ma he ru ka'i zhal du dam rdzas
NK033(gi)004:984: bdud rtsi 'bar ba'i mchod pa karma he ru ka'i
NK033(gi)004:985: zhal du dam rdzas bdud rtsi 'bar ba'i mchod pa
NK033(gi)004:986: he ru ka mngon rdzogs rgyal po'i zhal du dam
NK033(gi)004:987: rdzas bdud rtsi 'bar ba'i mchod pa zhing las skyes
NK033(gi)004:990: dur khrod chen po brgyad na gnas pa'i mkha' 'gro ma dang /
NK033(gi)004:991: mkha' 'gro ma 'bar ba'i gdong can 'khor dang bcas
NK033(gi)004:992: pa rnams kyi zhal du dam rdzas bdud rtsi 'bar
NK033(gi)004:993: ba'i mchod pa las las skyes pa'i mkha' 'gro ma
NK033(gi)004:994: / bud+d+ha rigs kyi mkha' 'gro ma dang /
NK033(gi)004:995: rdo rje rigs kyi mkha' 'gro ma dang /
NK033(gi)004:996: rin po che'i rigs kyi mkha' 'gro ma dang /
NK033(gi)004:997: pad+ma'i rigs kyi mkha' 'gro ma dang /
NK033(gi)004:998: las kyi rigs kyi mkha' 'gro ma dang /
NK033(gi)004:999: mkha' la gshegs ma 'khor dang bcas pa rnams kyi
NK033(gi)004:1000: zhal du dam rdzas bdud rtsi 'bar ba'i mchod pa
NK033(gi)004:1001: sngags las skyes pa'i mkha' 'gro ma /
NK033(gi)004:1004: sman mo lnga bcu rtsa brgyad /
NK033(gi)004:1005: dbang mo nyi shu rtsa brgyad /
NK033(gi)004:1010: mkha' 'gro ma mkha' la spyod ma 'khor dang bcas
NK033(gi)004:1011: pa rnams kyi zhal du dam rdzas bdud rtsi 'bar
NK033(gi)004:1012: ba'i gtor ma bzhes shig kha ram kh+aa hi /
NK033(gi)004:1013: gzhan yang bka' dang bstan pa srung zhing 'khor dang
NK033(gi)004:1014: gang zag skyong ba'i mgon po dam tshig can thams
NK033(gi)004:1015: cad la / dam rdzas bdud rtsi'i rgyan gyis brgyan pa'i 'bar ba'i gtor ma 'di 'bul lo //
NK033(gi)004:1019: mchod sbyin gtor ma 'di bzhes la //
NK033(gi)004:1020: sogs kyis phrin las spyi ltar bcol lo //
NK033(gi)004:1021: de yan chad sgrub thabs kyi dngos gazhi'o //
NK033(gi)004:1022: drug pa bza' ba tshogs kyi lung du tshogs 'bul ba la don bdun gyis bstan te /
NK033(gi)004:1023: dang po tshogs rnam pa gsum gyi sta gon du bya ba la /
NK033(gi)004:1024: dgyes ldan lha'i tshogs spyan drangs pa ni 'og tu bstan /
NK033(gi)004:1025: skal ldan mi'i tshogs dam ldan gyi rnal 'byor tshogs pas /
NK033(gi)004:1026: 'byor ldan yo byad kyi tshogs ci 'byor pa bsham mo //
NK033(gi)004:1027: gnyis pa bsang thabs rnam pa gsum gyis dri ma dag par bya ba ni /
NK033(gi)004:1029: ram ram ram ni ye shes me yin te //
NK033(gi)004:1030: me yi snying po ram zhes bya //
NK033(gi)004:1031: ram las ye shes me byung bas //
NK033(gi)004:1032: bag chags ma lus bsreg par bya //
NK033(gi)004:1034: yam yam yam ni ye shes rlung yin te //
NK033(gi)004:1035: rlung gi snying po yam zhes bya //
NK033(gi)004:1036: yam las ye shes rlung byung bas //
NK033(gi)004:1037: bag chags ma lus gtor bar bya //
NK033(gi)004:1039: kham kham kham ni ye shes chu yin te //
NK033(gi)004:1040: chu yi snying po kham zhes bya //
NK033(gi)004:1041: kham las ye shes chu byung bas //
NK033(gi)004:1042: bag chags ma lus bkru bar bya //
NK033(gi)004:1044: gsum pa sbyong thabs rnam pa gsum gyis dngos po dang mtshan ma med par sbyang ba ni /
NK033(gi)004:1046: lhag mthong gi me yis bsregs /
NK033(gi)004:1047: ye shes kyi rlung gis gtor //
NK033(gi)004:1048: zhi gnas kyi chu yis bkrus pas dngos 'dzin gyi dri ma mtha' dag stong par gyur /
NK033(gi)004:1049: bzhi pa byin rlabs rnam pa gsum gyis khyad par gyi rdzas su brlab pa ni /
NK033(gi)004:1051: tshogs gtor rin po che'i mchod sdong nor bu'i rgyal po dgos 'dod char bzhin du 'bebs pa dang /
NK033(gi)004:1052: gzugs sgra dri ro reg bya'i lha mo mchod rdzas thogs pas nam mkha'i khams gang ba dang /
NK033(gi)004:1053: bdud rtsi'i rgya mtsho mu tig dri ma med pa'i
NK033(gi)004:1054: kha dog lta bu zad mi shes pa'i gter chen
NK033(gi)004:1055: por gyur / +aahmh'u su ra to ma h+aa pany+tsa sh+r+ai he ru ka /
NK033(gi)004:1056: man+t+ra dz+wa la ma d+ha la /
NK033(gi)004:1061: ma h+aa sa ma ya phata /
NK033(gi)004:1062: ru lu ru lu h+aum b+h+yo h+aum /
NK033(gi)004:1064: mi dmigs mkha' ltar dag cing khyab pa'i sku //
NK033(gi)004:1065: spyan 'dren gshegs su gsol bar mi dmigs kyang //
NK033(gi)004:1066: thugs rje'i ngang nyid chos sku dag pa las //
NK033(gi)004:1067: ye shes sgyu mar rol cing gshegs su gsol //
NK033(gi)004:1069: dbang phyug chen po yab yum dang //
NK033(gi)004:1070: byang chub rdo rje lcam dral dang //
NK033(gi)004:1071: khro bo'i rgyal po mtha' dag dang //
NK033(gi)004:1072: ma mo mkha' 'gro'i tshogs dang bcas //
NK033(gi)004:1073: lha dang lha min rnal 'byor pa //
NK033(gi)004:1074: rnal 'byor longs spyod che la gshegs su gsol //
NK033(gi)004:1075: dzahmh'u bam hoh sh+r+ai he ru ka dri sh+ya hoh sa ma ya hoh sa ma ya s+t+wam /
NK033(gi)004:1078: lnga pa spro thabs rnam pa gsum gyis dmigs pa so sor bzung ba ni /
NK033(gi)004:1079: ral gris tshogs rdzas rnams tsho gsum du bgos la /
NK033(gi)004:1081: 'di ni shes rab ral gri ste //
NK033(gi)004:1082: rin chen gter kha 'byed pa dang //
NK033(gi)004:1084: dri med bdud rtsi 'byung ba dang //
NK033(gi)004:1085: dgra bgegs srog rtsa gcod pa dang //
NK033(gi)004:1086: dug lnga rtsad nas bcad pa'i phyir //
NK033(gi)004:1087: srog can rgyu dang srog med rgyu //
NK033(gi)004:1088: 'di ni srog med rgyu yin te //
NK033(gi)004:1089: snying rje med pas bsgral bar bya //
NK033(gi)004:1090: zhes zhal gsum du 'bul ba'i rdzas 'dod yon bdud rtsi sha khrag tu dmigs /
NK033(gi)004:1091: drug pa dbul thabs rnam pa gsum gyis bdag gi don sgrub pa ni /
NK033(gi)004:1092: dang po g.yas zhal dkar ba la dmigs te zhi ba'i lha tshogs la mchod pa ni /
NK033(gi)004:1094: bla med mchog gi mchod pa dam pa sbyar ba 'di //
NK033(gi)004:1095: ye shes lnga yi 'od zer rnam par 'phro //
NK033(gi)004:1096: dbang po lnga yi longs spyod mkho dgur ldan //
NK033(gi)004:1097: 'dod pa'i yon tan lnga yis rab brgyan te //
NK033(gi)004:1098: thugs dam bzhin du ci bder bzhes su gsol //
NK033(gi)004:1100: gnyis pa g.yon zhal dmar po thugs rje gshe ba'i
NK033(gi)004:1101: lha tshogs la dmigs nas bshags pa 'bul ba ni
NK033(gi)004:1103: bdag cag ma rig lus dang ngag sems kyis //
NK033(gi)004:1104: bag med tshul gyis dam las 'gal gyur te //
NK033(gi)004:1105: lus kyis srog bcad sdig pa dngos su bgyis //
NK033(gi)004:1106: ngag gis rdzun smras gzhan la ngan du brjod //
NK033(gi)004:1107: sems kyis blo nor log par bsam la sogs //
NK033(gi)004:1108: 'dod khro gti mug dbang gis sdig pa ci bgyis pa //
NK033(gi)004:1109: bkram pa'i lha tshogs rnams la bzod par gsol //
NK033(gi)004:1110: ye shes lha la rtog pa mi mnga' yang //
NK033(gi)004:1111: de yi bka' 'khor gnas pa'i lha srin rnams //
NK033(gi)004:1112: 'di 'dra dmyal sogs shin tu mi bzod pas //
NK033(gi)004:1113: gnong zhing 'gal 'khrul mchis pa bzod par gsol //
NK033(gi)004:1115: gsum pa zhal dbus mthing ba la dmigs te khro
NK033(gi)004:1116: bo khrag 'thung gi tshogs la stob pa bya ba
NK033(gi)004:1118: nga ni za byed chen po ste //
NK033(gi)004:1119: khams gsum ma lus bza' ba'i phyir //
NK033(gi)004:1120: sha rus la sogs bza' bar bya //
NK033(gi)004:1122: nga ni khrag 'thung chen po ste //
NK033(gi)004:1123: 'khor ba'i d+r+wa bar chags pa dang //
NK033(gi)004:1124: dmar chen po la rgya mtshor bskyil //
NK033(gi)004:1125: 'khor gyi ma tshogs rnams dang rol //
NK033(gi)004:1126: dpal chen khrag 'thung he ru ka /
NK033(gi)004:1127: khro rgyal khrag 'thung rngam pa'i tshogs //
NK033(gi)004:1128: g.yo 'gul thams cad bsgral ba'i phyir //
NK033(gi)004:1129: gzugs rnams thams cad he ru ka /
NK033(gi)004:1130: koo r+ai la sogs za byed rnams //
NK033(gi)004:1131: sing+ha la sogs gsod byed tshogs //
NK033(gi)004:1132: rta gdong la sogs 'ching sdom tshogs //
NK033(gi)004:1133: dbang phyug la sogs bka' nyan tshogs //
NK033(gi)004:1134: pho nya la sogs 'joms byed tshogs //
NK033(gi)004:1135: choms shig 'khor ba rtsad nas chom //
NK033(gi)004:1136: ha ha ru lu mchod pa bzhes //
NK033(gi)004:1137: zhes zhal du bstab par bya'o //
NK033(gi)004:1138: bdun pa sbyong thabs rnam pa gsum gyis phrin las bcol ba ni /
NK033(gi)004:1139: tshogs zan ling gar bcos pa la rten byas te /
NK033(gi)004:1140: sdang dgra gdon bgegs su dmigs pa dang /
NK033(gi)004:1141: gnod sems kyi dug zhi bar byed pa dang /
NK033(gi)004:1142: nyon mongs pa lnga ye shes su sbyong bar byed pa'i sems kyis nga rgyal bskyed pa dang /
NK033(gi)004:1143: bden stobs 'gugs gzhug spyi mthun dang /
NK033(gi)004:1145: 'khor gyi dmag tshogs dam tshig can //
NK033(gi)004:1146: dam tshig tshul bzhin gshegs su gsol //
NK033(gi)004:1147: slob dpon la ni brnyas byed cing //
NK033(gi)004:1148: rdo rje spun la 'khu byed dang //
NK033(gi)004:1149: snying nas slob dpon smod byed rnams //
NK033(gi)004:1150: ma thogs myur du drag tu khug /
NK033(gi)004:1152: khro chung zhal gsum phyag drug pa //
NK033(gi)004:1153: mtshon cha'i rgyal po lcags kyu yis //
NK033(gi)004:1154: 'og min dga' ldan lha yul nas //
NK033(gi)004:1155: ngo mthon stobs kyis bsgral bar bya //
NK033(gi)004:1156: zhes brjod pas khro chung mang po 'phros nas dgra
NK033(gi)004:1157: bgegs gang na yod pa de lcags kyus bzung nas
NK033(gi)004:1158: gzugs de la thim par bsam la /
NK033(gi)004:1159: de nas rang nyid lha'i nga rgyal dang ldan pas
NK033(gi)004:1160: drag sngags so lnga pa brjod cing phur pa snying
NK033(gi)004:1162: 'khor ba rtsad nas bcad par bsam /
NK033(gi)004:1163: mtshon cha sna tshogs kyi sa ling ga de gtubs la /
NK033(gi)004:1164: khro bo'i lha tshogs rnams la bstab par bya ste /
NK033(gi)004:1167: 'jigs byed chen po'i tshul bstan pa //
NK033(gi)004:1168: dpal chen dgu dang yum chen dgu //
NK033(gi)004:1169: gnyis med sbyor ba'i byin rlabs las //
NK033(gi)004:1170: koo r+ai'i tshogs dang seng+ha'i tshogs //
NK033(gi)004:1171: sgo ma'i tshogs dang spor ma'i tshogs //
NK033(gi)004:1172: mkha' 'gro dbang phyug chen mo'i tshogs //
NK033(gi)004:1173: phung po dpal gyi zhal du bstabs //
NK033(gi)004:1174: 'byung ba yum gyi zhal du bstabs //
NK033(gi)004:1175: rnam shes koo r+ai'i zhal du bstabs //
NK033(gi)004:1176: yul ni phra men zhal du bstabs //
NK033(gi)004:1177: yan lag sgo ma'i zhal du bstabs //
NK033(gi)004:1178: rus pa mkha' 'gro'i zhal du bstabs //
NK033(gi)004:1179: khrag ni ma mo'i zhal du bstabs //
NK033(gi)004:1180: sha ni pho nya'i zhal du bstabs //
NK033(gi)004:1181: srog ni ging chen zhal du bstabs //
NK033(gi)004:1182: lhag ma 'khor gyi zhal du bstabs //
NK033(gi)004:1183: yas kyi bdud g.yos mchod par bzhes //
NK033(gi)004:1184: mas kyi sri langs mchod par bzhes //
NK033(gi)004:1185: pha khu'i rgan sri mchod par bzhes //
NK033(gi)004:1186: ma bu'i byur 'dre mchod par bzhes //
NK033(gi)004:1187: bu tsha'i phung sri mchod par bzhes //
NK033(gi)004:1188: rnal 'byor dam sri mchod par bzhes //
NK033(gi)004:1189: sdang ba'i dgra rnams mchod par bzhes //
NK033(gi)004:1190: gnod pa'i bgegs rnams mchod par bzhes //
NK033(gi)004:1191: sngags kyi sngags zor mchod par bzhes //
NK033(gi)004:1192: chos kyi chos zor mchod par bzhes //
NK033(gi)004:1193: bon gyi bon zor mchod par bzhes //
NK033(gi)004:1194: rgya 'dre stong mtshams mchod par bzhes //
NK033(gi)004:1195: rmi lam ngan pa mchod par bzhes //
NK033(gi)004:1196: mtshan ma ngan pa mchod par bzhes //
NK033(gi)004:1197: sbyor ba rtsub pa mchod par bzhes //
NK033(gi)004:1198: lo skag zla zur mchod par bzhes //
NK033(gi)004:1199: za skag bdud zhag mchod par bzhes //
NK033(gi)004:1200: mi mthun phyogs rnams mchod par bzhes //
NK033(gi)004:1201: mchod bzhes dam skongs mthu rtsal dngos grub stsol //
NK033(gi)004:1202: zhes ling ga gtub pa de gtor mar dbul lo //
NK033(gi)004:1203: bdun pa lhag ma mjug sdud kyi lung du lhag
NK033(gi)004:1204: ma sdud cing gtor ma'i mjug bskyang ba la phud
NK033(gi)004:1205: dang lhag ma'i mtshams sbyor ba ni /
NK033(gi)004:1207: bcom ldan dpal chen 'khor dang bcas pa rnams //
NK033(gi)004:1208: nam mkha'i mtha' dang mnyam pa'i sku mnga' ba //
NK033(gi)004:1209: mi 'jigs sku yi dngos grub stsal tu gsol //
NK033(gi)004:1210: chags med pad+ma 'dra ba'i spyan mnga' ba //
NK033(gi)004:1211: ma chags gsung gi dngos grub stsal tu gsol //
NK033(gi)004:1212: 'gro drug thugs rjes sgrol ba'i thugs mnga' ba //
NK033(gi)004:1213: skye med thugs kyi dngos grub stsal tu gsol //
NK033(gi)004:1214: 'gro drug smin mdzad bde ba'i don sgrub pa //
NK033(gi)004:1215: phrin las rtsal gyi dngos grub stsal tu gsol //
NK033(gi)004:1216: zhes brjod la mig btsum nas dmod bor la tshogs
NK033(gi)004:1217: gtor gyi nang nas gcig dngos grub tu blangs la
NK033(gi)004:1218: bza' / de'ang sha la babs na mthu che /
NK033(gi)004:1221: mar la rtogs pa che bar bshad do //
NK033(gi)004:1222: de nas tshogs rdzas rnams nang gi sbyin sreg tu
NK033(gi)004:1223: longs spyad pa'i lhag ma la tshogs phud dang po
NK033(gi)004:1224: dang bar pa'i cha shas bsre /
NK033(gi)004:1225: bdud rtsi'i kha phru btab la /
NK033(gi)004:1226: rang nyid dpal chen por gsal ba'i ya rkan dang
NK033(gi)004:1227: ma rkan rta mgrin yab yum du gsal ba'i sbyor
NK033(gi)004:1228: mtshams nas byang sems dkar dmar gyi rgyun babs /
NK033(gi)004:1229: lhag gtor gyi mi gtsang ba'i dri ma sbyangs /
NK033(gi)004:1230: bdud rtsi rgya mtsho 'dod pa'i yon tan lnga'i sprin 'phro bar gyur /
NK033(gi)004:1233: rang gi thugs ka nas 'od zer 'phros /
NK033(gi)004:1234: lhag mgron mar gyi gnas bdun g.yog dang bcas pa
NK033(gi)004:1235: skad cig gis spyan drangs te mdun du 'khod par
NK033(gi)004:1237: nam mkha' stong la dbang bsgyur ba'i //
NK033(gi)004:1238: mkha' 'gro sum cu rtsa gnyis kyang //
NK033(gi)004:1240: rnam lnga'i longs spyod 'di bzhes la //
NK033(gi)004:1241: 'jig rten las kun khyod la bcol //
NK033(gi)004:1242: bcol ba'i phrin las sgrub par mdzod //
NK033(gi)004:1244: 'jig rten bya ba las grub pa'i //
NK033(gi)004:1245: 'bar ma lang ka'i rgya mtsho yang //
NK033(gi)004:1247: rnam lnga'i longs spyod 'di bzhes la //
NK033(gi)004:1248: 'jig rten las kun khyod la bcol //
NK033(gi)004:1249: bcol ba'i phrin las sgrub par mdzod //
NK033(gi)004:1250: phyogs bcur mgyogs pa'i las byed pa'i //
NK033(gi)004:1251: pho nya sum brgya drug cu yang //
NK033(gi)004:1253: rnam lnga'i longs spyod 'di bzhes la //
NK033(gi)004:1254: 'jig rten las kun khyod la bcol //
NK033(gi)004:1255: bcol ba'i phrin las sgrub par mdzod //
NK033(gi)004:1256: ta kri ta lcam mor zhal bzhes pa'i //
NK033(gi)004:1257: 'bar ma chen mo brgyad rnams kyang //
NK033(gi)004:1259: rnam lnga'i longs spyod 'di bzhes la //
NK033(gi)004:1260: 'jig rten las kun khyod la bcol //
NK033(gi)004:1261: bcol ba'i phrin las sgrub par mdzod //
NK033(gi)004:1262: sha khrag zhal du gsol byed pa'i //
NK033(gi)004:1263: dur khrod dregs pa'i ma bdun yang //
NK033(gi)004:1265: rnam lnga'i longs spyod 'di bzhes la //
NK033(gi)004:1266: 'jig rten las kun khyod la bcol //
NK033(gi)004:1267: bcol ba'i phrin las sgrub par mdzod //
NK033(gi)004:1268: rgyal chen sring mor zhal bzhes pa'i //
NK033(gi)004:1269: sring mo chen mo bzhi rnams kyang //
NK033(gi)004:1271: rnam lnga'i longs spyod 'di bzhes la //
NK033(gi)004:1272: 'jig rten las kun khyod la bcol //
NK033(gi)004:1273: bcol ba'i phrin las sgrub par mdzod //
NK033(gi)004:1274: ri rab rmangs nas 'degs byed pa'i //
NK033(gi)004:1275: dbang gi gru 'degs chen mo bzhi //
NK033(gi)004:1277: rnam lnga'i longs spyod 'di bzhes la //
NK033(gi)004:1278: 'jig rten las kun khyod la bcol //
NK033(gi)004:1279: bcol ba'i phrin las sgrub par mdzod //
NK033(gi)004:1280: pha rol dmag dpung 'joms mdzad pa'i //
NK033(gi)004:1281: dmag gi rgyal mo mched bzhi yang //
NK033(gi)004:1283: rnam lnga'i longs spyod 'di bzhes la //
NK033(gi)004:1284: 'jig rten las kun khyod la bcol //
NK033(gi)004:1285: bcol ba'i phrin las sgrub par mdzod //
NK033(gi)004:1286: chos skyong srung mar dam bcas pa'i //
NK033(gi)004:1287: bod khams brtan ma bcu gnyis kyang //
NK033(gi)004:1289: rnam lnga'i longs spyod 'di bzhes la //
NK033(gi)004:1290: 'jig rten las kun khyod la bcol //
NK033(gi)004:1291: bcol ba'i phrin las sgrub par mdzod //
NK033(gi)004:1292: +amo badz+ra ka la sa pa si b+h+yo /
NK033(gi)004:1293: zhes lhag ma phyi rol tu 'bul lo //
NK033(gi)004:1294: de nas gtor ma tsho gsum du bgos te /
NK033(gi)004:1295: chos dbyings kyi gtor ma gter du sbed pa ni /
NK033(gi)004:1297: thugs rje rang byung ye shes dkyil 'khor du //
NK033(gi)004:1298: snang srid mtshan ma'i bye brag kun //
NK033(gi)004:1299: snod kyi 'jig rten dbyings su sba //
NK033(gi)004:1300: snod kyang bcud kyi dbyings su sba //
NK033(gi)004:1301: snod bcud skye ba med par sba //
NK033(gi)004:1302: srid pa za byed gzhal yas khang //
NK033(gi)004:1303: rtsi shing bdud rtsi rang byung ste //
NK033(gi)004:1304: 'byung ba lnga dang rigs lnga yang //
NK033(gi)004:1305: chos nyid stong pa'i dbyings su sba //
NK033(gi)004:1306: nyon mongs dug lnga'i ngo bo yang //
NK033(gi)004:1307: ye shes lnga yi dbyings su sba //
NK033(gi)004:1308: ma rig 'khrul pa'i log rtog kyang //
NK033(gi)004:1309: mnyam snang chen po'i dbyings su sba //
NK033(gi)004:1310: rdzas rnams byang chub sems su bsgom //
NK033(gi)004:1311: sngags mkhan theg mchog rgyal por bsgoms la gtor ma
NK033(gi)004:1312: cha gcig po dkyil 'khor gyi gzhi la gter du
NK033(gi)004:1313: sba / phyag rgya lngas rgyas gdab la bro brdung /
NK033(gi)004:1316: dngos grub 'byung ba'i dgos pa yod par gsungs /
NK033(gi)004:1317: de nas ye shes rol pa'i gtor ma sbyin sreg tu 'bul ba ni /
NK033(gi)004:1318: bla ma yi dam mkha' 'gro rnams me thab kyi gzhal yas khang du bskyed la /
NK033(gi)004:1319: tshogs gtor cha gcig me mchod dam sbyin sreg gi tshul du 'bul lo //
NK033(gi)004:1320: thugs rje sprul pa'i gtor ma 'gro ba rnams la
NK033(gi)004:1321: phan gdags shing phrin las rnam bzhi'i don 'grub par
NK033(gi)004:1322: bya ba'i phyir srung ma la bskyangs te /
NK033(gi)004:1323: dri bzang gis byugs pa'i man+dala la tshogs gtor cha gcig bzhag nas /
NK033(gi)004:1325: shar nas gshegs pa'i rnal 'byor bdun //
NK033(gi)004:1326: shar phyogs rdo rje rigs kyi bka' nyan tshogs //
NK033(gi)004:1327: drug ni rnal 'byor gral na bzhugs //
NK033(gi)004:1328: gcig ni thabs kyi sgo ma mdzad //
NK033(gi)004:1329: dkar mo dung gi mche ba can //
NK033(gi)004:1330: phyag na dung gi gzhong pa bsnams //
NK033(gi)004:1331: rgyan gyi gtor ma 'di longs la //
NK033(gi)004:1332: khyed kyis zhi ba'i las mdzod cig /
NK033(gi)004:1334: rgyu sbyor yon bdag pho mo yi //
NK033(gi)004:1335: bgegs rnams bsrung ba rkyen rnams bzlog /
NK033(gi)004:1337: lho nas gshegs pa'i rnal 'byor bdun //
NK033(gi)004:1338: rin chen rigs kyi bka' nyan tshogs //
NK033(gi)004:1339: drug ni rnal 'byor gral na bzhugs //
NK033(gi)004:1340: gcig ni thabs kyi sgo ma mdzad //
NK033(gi)004:1341: ser mo gser gyi mche ba can //
NK033(gi)004:1342: phyag na gser gyi gzhong pa bsnams //
NK033(gi)004:1343: rgyan gyi gtor ma 'di longs la //
NK033(gi)004:1344: khyod kyis rgyas pa'i las mdzod cig /
NK033(gi)004:1346: rgyu sbyor yon bdag pho mo yi //
NK033(gi)004:1347: bgegs rnams bsrung la rkyen rnams bzlog /
NK033(gi)004:1349: nub nas gshegs pa'i rnal 'byor bdun //
NK033(gi)004:1350: pad+ma rigs kyi bka' nyan tshogs //
NK033(gi)004:1351: drug ni rnal 'byor gral na bzhugs //
NK033(gi)004:1352: gcig ni thabs kyi sgo ma mdzad //
NK033(gi)004:1353: dmar mo bswe yi mche ba can //
NK033(gi)004:1354: phyag na bswe yi gzhong pa bsnams //
NK033(gi)004:1355: rgyan gyi gtor ma 'di longs la //
NK033(gi)004:1356: khyed kyis dbang gi las mdzod cig /
NK033(gi)004:1358: rgyu sbyor yon bdag pho mo yi //
NK033(gi)004:1359: bgegs rnams bsrung la rkyen rnams bzlog /
NK033(gi)004:1361: byang nas gshegs pa'i rnal 'byor bdun //
NK033(gi)004:1362: las kyi rigs kyi bka' nyan tshogs //
NK033(gi)004:1363: drug ni rnal 'byor gral na bzhugs //
NK033(gi)004:1364: gcig ni thabs kyi sgo ma mdzad //
NK033(gi)004:1365: sngon mo g.yu yi mche ba can //
NK033(gi)004:1366: phyag na g.yu yi gzhong pa bsnams //
NK033(gi)004:1367: rgyan gyi gtor ma 'di longs la //
NK033(gi)004:1368: khyod kyis drag po'i las mdzod cig /
NK033(gi)004:1370: rgyu sbyor yon bdag pho mo yi //
NK033(gi)004:1371: bgegs rnams bsrung la rkyen rnams bzlog /
NK033(gi)004:1372: ces gtor ma sa gtsang sar spungs /
NK033(gi)004:1373: dri ma yal bar du sdud du mi gzhug go //
NK033(gi)004:1374: gtor snod de rnams cha gsum du phye la cha gcig ma bshal bar kha yar bstan la bzhag /
NK033(gi)004:1375: nang du nas sam me tog gis bkang la dkon mchog la dbul /
NK033(gi)004:1376: des bkra shis pa'i dgos pa yod /
NK033(gi)004:1377: cha gcig bshal chu phyir dor /
NK033(gi)004:1378: bshal chu re ba'i yi dwags tshim zhing kho thag chod pa'i dgos pa yod /
NK033(gi)004:1379: cha gcig mi bshal bar kha sbubs la /
NK033(gi)004:1380: dgra bgegs ting nge 'dzin gyis bkug la 'og tu bcug ste /
NK033(gi)004:1381: bro brdung la mnan pa bya'o //
NK033(gi)004:1382: bar chad zhi nas dgra bgegs mi ldang ba'i dgos pa yod /
NK033(gi)004:1383: las kyi mjug bsdu bro brdung /
NK033(gi)004:1384: mnan pa byed pa'i dus su byin dbab cing /
NK033(gi)004:1386: dang po byin dbab pa ni /
NK033(gi)004:1387: a la la hoh b+ha ga w+aan /
NK033(gi)004:1388: sa ma ya hoh sa ma ya s+t+wam /
NK033(gi)004:1390: 'phags mchog thugs rje can gyi dus la bab //
NK033(gi)004:1391: khyad par bstan pa'i dus la bab //
NK033(gi)004:1392: dgra bgegs 'dul ba'i dus la bab //
NK033(gi)004:1393: byin chen dbab pa'i dus la bab //
NK033(gi)004:1394: mthu chen mthu stsol bcol ldan 'das //
NK033(gi)004:1395: dbang chen dbang bskur bcom ldan 'das //
NK033(gi)004:1396: byin chen byin phob bcom ldan 'das //
NK033(gi)004:1397: dngos grub mchog stsol bcom ldan 'das //
NK033(gi)004:1398: bdag cag las kyi 'bras bu mchis par mdzod //
NK033(gi)004:1400: de nas bro brdung ba ni /
NK033(gi)004:1401: gtor gzhong kha sbubs pa'i 'og tu dgra bgegs bkug la /
NK033(gi)004:1403: stong gsum stong gi 'jig rten na //
NK033(gi)004:1404: kun kyang bud+d+ha he ru ka /
NK033(gi)004:1405: bud+d+ha kro d+h+ai shwa r+ai s+t+wam //
NK033(gi)004:1406: khro bo'i sprul pas nam mkha' gang //
NK033(gi)004:1407: khro mo'i sprul pas sa gzhi gang //
NK033(gi)004:1408: khro chung sprul pas bar snang gang //
NK033(gi)004:1409: ma mo mkha' 'gro dbyings na rol //
NK033(gi)004:1410: lta ba'i ngang la gnas pa'i phyir //
NK033(gi)004:1411: bro ni bar chad med pa'i bro //
NK033(gi)004:1412: tshangs pa'i dbyangs su 'dren pa'i phyir //
NK033(gi)004:1413: glu ni bar chad med par blangs //
NK033(gi)004:1414: dkyil 'khor rang la gnas pa'i phyir //
NK033(gi)004:1415: tshig ni snying po 'dzab tu bgrangs //
NK033(gi)004:1416: ru lu ru lu h'u b+h+yo h'u /
NK033(gi)004:1417: nyon mongs lnga la bro brdungs pas //
NK033(gi)004:1418: dug lnga'i steng du sman lnga shar //
NK033(gi)004:1419: nga rgyal sa la bro brdungs pas //
NK033(gi)004:1420: nga rgyal spangs nas mnyam nyid shar //
NK033(gi)004:1421: 'dod chags chu la bro brdungs pas //
NK033(gi)004:1422: 'dod chags spangs nas bde chen shar //
NK033(gi)004:1423: zhe sdang me la bro brdungs pas //
NK033(gi)004:1424: zhe sdang spangs nas stong nyid shar //
NK033(gi)004:1425: phrag dog rlung la bro brdungs pas //
NK033(gi)004:1426: phrag dog spangs nas mnyam nyid shar //
NK033(gi)004:1427: gti mug nam mkhar bro brdungs pas //
NK033(gi)004:1428: gti mug spangs nas ye shes shar //
NK033(gi)004:1429: ru lu ru lu h'u b+h+yo h'u /
NK033(gi)004:1430: khri gdugs brgya shar stong shar bas //
NK033(gi)004:1431: ye shes nyi ma gcig shar dro //
NK033(gi)004:1432: shar tsam nyid nas nub pa med //
NK033(gi)004:1433: nga ni dpal chen he ru ka /
NK033(gi)004:1434: rkang pa g.yas pas bro brdungs pas //
NK033(gi)004:1435: rnal 'byor pho sri mnan pa'i bro //
NK033(gi)004:1436: rkang pa g.yon pas bro brdungs pas //
NK033(gi)004:1437: rnal 'byor mo sri mnan pa'i bro //
NK033(gi)004:1438: rkang pa gnyis kas bro brdungs pas //
NK033(gi)004:1439: rgyab nyan rkun bu mnan pa'i bro //
NK033(gi)004:1440: rmig pa lcags kyis bro brdungs pas //
NK033(gi)004:1441: sa bdag sa sri mnan pa'i bro //
NK033(gi)004:1442: sba' ma de ni mi sba ru //
NK033(gi)004:1443: rgya mtsho chen po'i gting du sba //
NK033(gi)004:1444: mnan nam de ni mi mnan na //
NK033(gi)004:1445: ri rab chen po'i rmangs su mnan //
NK033(gi)004:1446: bskal pa brgyar yang ma ldang zhig /
NK033(gi)004:1448: rgya la 'da' na rdul du rlog /
NK033(gi)004:1450: s+t+wam b+ha rak+sha m+aa ra ya nan /
NK033(gi)004:1452: 'di la rjes chog mchod bstod ma bshad pas dgos
NK033(gi)004:1453: par ma mngon kyang rtogs bsam 'chun na spyi ltar
NK033(gi)004:1454: mdor bsdus dang / nongs bshags bzod gsol bya /
NK033(gi)004:1455: bkra shis rgyas par brjod cing rol mo bsgrag /
NK033(gi)004:1456: rang don la ye shes pa mi gshegs /
NK033(gi)004:1457: gzhan don la gshegs par bshad /
NK033(gi)004:1458: tshogs mgron sogs rten dang ras bris yod na brtan bzhugs gsol /
NK033(gi)004:1459: dam tshig gi dkyil 'khor gzhal yas khang dang bcas pa gtso bo la thim /
NK033(gi)004:1460: gtso bo thugs srog +amo la bsdu /
NK033(gi)004:1461: de nyid gyen rdzogs su rim par bsdus nas thig le la thim /
NK033(gi)004:1462: de'ang 'od gsal gyi dbyings su yal bar gyur /
NK033(gi)004:1463: ces bsgom la brda bzhi tshul bzhi dang ldan pas rdzogs rim gyi rtogs pa yun ring bskyang /
NK033(gi)004:1464: slar skad cig gis dpal chen mngon rdzogs rgyal po'i skur gyur pa'i dpral bar +amo /
NK033(gi)004:1466: lus thams cad rdo rje'i go chas gtams par gyur par bsam la rtsa sngags ru lu bcas brjod /
NK033(gi)004:1467: bsngo smon khyad par can gyis mtha' brgyan par bya'o //
NK033(gi)004:1468: 'di'i thog ma'i rgya mtsho khrus lung ni las thams
NK033(gi)004:1469: cad kyi sngon du 'gro ba yin pas rnam pa
NK033(gi)004:1470: kun tu grub na legs shing /
NK033(gi)004:1471: sgo gsum las kyi spyod pa ni phrin chog dkyus tsam la ma grub kyang chog go //
NK033(gi)004:1472: deng dus phal cher chos la dbang za zhing //
NK033(gi)004:1473: rtog ges snyems rnams 'di 'drar brnyas thabs rtsom //
NK033(gi)004:1474: gzhan dag gal chung snyoms las kho nas g.yengs //
NK033(gi)004:1475: tshul 'dir byi dor bgyid pa shin tu dkon //
NK033(gi)004:1476: de phyir lhag pa'i bsam pas kun bslangs shing //
NK033(gi)004:1477: rang blon gang dbogs gsal bar bkod na yang //
NK033(gi)004:1478: nongs pa gang mchis rtsa gsum chos srung la //
NK033(gi)004:1479: snying nas bshags so dag tshangs byin rlabs stsol //
NK033(gi)004:1480: dge bas skye ba 'di dang skye ba gzhan //
NK033(gi)004:1481: 'od gsal rdo rje'i snying po'i skal ldan du //
NK033(gi)004:1482: gyur nas gzhon nu bum skur mngon byang chub //
NK033(gi)004:1483: khams gsum 'gro rnams dbyings su sgrol byed shog /
NK033(gi)004:1484: 'di'i gzhung gi yig rnying la mngon rtogs mi gsal
NK033(gi)004:1485: zhing yig nor rgyun 'byams su mngon pa'ang mang zhig
NK033(gi)004:1487: khyab bdag kun mkhyen bla ma rin po che 'jam dbyangs mkhyen brtse'i dbang po'i zhal snga nas /
NK033(gi)004:1488: chog bsgrigs kha gsal zhig cis kyang 'os pa'i bka'i gnang ba stsal ba dang /
NK033(gi)004:1489: rang 'dra'i blo dman la phan du re bas /
NK033(gi)004:1490: phrin las sgrub thabs lhan thabs mchan rnying rnams kyi
NK033(gi)004:1491: dgongs pa bstun te bklag chog gi tshul du karma
NK033(gi)004:1492: ngag dbang yon tan rgya matsho'am /
NK033(gi)004:1493: blo gros mtha' yas pa'i sdes rdzong shod bde gshegs
